INSERT INTO `blog` VALUES (7,8,'陈菊邀北京市长访高雄 默认访大陆有破冰意义','<h3>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 环球时报驻台北特约撰稿人韦博报道，民进党籍高雄市长陈菊今天抵达北京访问。她表示，欢迎北京市长在高雄世运期间到高雄参观访问。她也承认此行具有&ldquo;破冰意义&rdquo;。</h3>\r\n<p>　　据台湾&ldquo;中央社&rdquo;消息，陈菊下午2时许在下榻的北京饭店接受媒体采访表示，台湾承办2009年世界运动会，高雄作为承办城市，有责任也有义务到所有世运总会重要国家和地区进行营销，北京和上海是第6站和第7站。</p>\r\n<p>　　她表示，此行没有替民进党主席蔡英文转达民进党与大陆沟通交流的讯息。她说，此行非常单纯，作为承办世运城市的市长，欢迎北京市市长还有北京市民朋友在世运期间到高雄参观访问。</p>\r\n<p>　　陈菊被问到作为民进党现任在职最高行政首长到大陆访问是否有&ldquo;破冰&rdquo;或象征意义，她说，&ldquo;如果你们要这样认为我也没有意见，我也接受。&rdquo;</p>','2009-05-22 09:10:04'),(8,8,'田震助阵《潘作良》首映成焦点 首次谈病情(图)','<center><img alt=\"田震助阵《潘作良》首映成焦点首次谈病情(图)\" src=\"http://i3.sinaimg.cn/ent/m/c/2009-05-26/1243274801_Iak1re.jpg\" border=\"1\" /></center><center>田震在昨天的发布会上表示，自己正通过打羽毛球进行恢复。本报记者 郭延冰 摄</center>\r\n<p>　　本报讯 （记者孙琳琳）新中国成立60周年献礼片<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/f/panzuoliang/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">《潘作良》</font></a>于昨日在政协礼堂举行了隆重的首映式，导演及主演在演员<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/h/f/wengh.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">翁虹</font></a>、歌手<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/f/mn.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">毛宁</font></a>、主持人<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/f/shjy/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">水均益</font></a>等庞大明星阵容的助阵下亮相。不过昨日首映式上的焦点无一是因传出患上血液病而沉寂两年的<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/f/tianz.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">田震</font></a>，她是以影片主题曲演唱者的身份出席本次活动的，田震也坦率地主动开口谈起病情：&ldquo;我很好。&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>　　影片《潘作良》是以已故辽宁省辽中县信访局长潘作良的事迹改编，选取了潘作良生前成功化解的百余疑难上访案件中的四个典型故事。据悉，该片将于6月2日在全国上映。</p>\r\n<p>　　该片的主题歌演唱者田震的现身成为首映式上媒体关注的焦点，她曾因患上慢性血液病而突然淡出歌坛，此次也是她患病后首次公开亮相。虽然脸色还不是很好，但田震的精神很不错，她主动谈起病情：&ldquo;我很好，谢谢大家的关心。&rdquo;此外，她也对<a class=\"akey\" href=\"http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/f/mwj.html\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"#000099\">满文军</font></a>吸毒表示&ldquo;很遗憾&rdquo;。据悉，目前田震已经开始打羽毛球进行恢复性训练，她自己也希望尽快推出新专辑。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: red\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>','2009-05-26 14:41:00'),(13,8,'大家好好休息！','<p><span style=\"font-size: large\"><span style=\"font-family: 黑体\">明天放假了！大家好好休息！</span></span></p>','2009-05-27 14:48:29'),(14,8,'北京第六例甲型流感患','<p>本报讯（记者李秋萌）昨天，本市再确诊两例输入性甲型H1N1流感病例，其中一名患者是54岁的美国籍教师鲍女士，一名患者是23岁的留美学生李某，分别于5月26日、27日乘机到达北京。这也是本市第六例和第七例输入性流感病例。。</p>\r\n<p>　　卫生部门紧急寻找与患者鲍女士同乘大巴（京B08455）去长城及十三陵游玩的乘客。联系电话64212461或12320。</p>\r\n<p>　　此外，目前全市有75人接受集中医学观察。</p>\r\n<p>　　鲍女士现就职于美国某大学社会学系。她和3名同伴乘坐UA851(座位号D18)航班自美国芝加哥起飞，5月26日下午到达首都机场。</p>\r\n<p>　　据患者本人反映，28日晚餐后发现不适，自测体温37.2摄氏度，后接到东城区东外保健科医生的电话告知，一行4人接受了健康监测，并得到保健科医生的健康宣传的指导。5月29日，一行4人在酒店休息，未外出。鲍女士自行服药后未见好转，体温最高38.1摄氏度。东外保健科医生为其拨打120电话，将其送至军区总医院发热门诊就诊。后经市疾控中心实验室检测，结果为甲型H1N1流感病毒核酸阳性。</p>\r\n<p>　　28日，患者曾从天安门乘大巴到长城及十三陵游览。</p>\r\n<p>　<strong>　第六例部分行程26日抵达T3航站楼，乘机场快线进城。</strong></p>\r\n<p>　　28日从天安门的北京旅游集散中心乘坐大巴前往长城及十三陵游览。大巴车号：京B08455</p>\r\n<p>　　密切接触者</p>\r\n<p>　　酒店工作人员、餐厅服务员、共同旅游人员、出租车司机等。</p>\r\n<p><strong>　　第七例 乘C089航班抵京</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>　　密接者仅为父母二人</strong></p>\r\n<p>　　患者李某现就读于美国新泽西州某大学，27日下午抵京（C089航班，座位号45L），由父亲自驾车接回家。</p>\r\n<p>　　28日下午曾由其父驾车前往奥林匹克公园游玩，未在外就餐。</p>\r\n<p>　　29日早上患者出现发热、肌肉酸疼症状，自测体温37.5摄氏度，自行服药未见好转；晚上父亲自驾车前往海淀医院发热门诊就诊，当天未有其他外出活动。经调查判定，其密切接触者为其父母二人。</p>\r\n<p>　　29日23时30分，海淀区疾控中心采集患者及其父母咽拭子标本，送市疾控中心实验室进行检测，李某标本呈甲型H1N1流感病毒核酸阳性；其父母标本呈阴性。</p>\r\n<p>　　目前患者已进行隔离治疗，患者父母目前无不适症状，已经接受医学观察。</p>','2009-05-31 09:08:09'),(19,24,'Nutch入门教程一','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;\r\nfont-weight:normal\">1.</span></strong><strong><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">什么是</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-weight:normal\">Nutch<o:p></o:p></span></strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Nutch&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">是一个开源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Java&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">实现的搜索引擎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">你可以在这里找到它：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch.apache.org</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">可分为爬虫（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawler</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）和查询（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">searcher</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Crawler</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">主要用于从网络上抓取网页并为这些网页建立索引。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Searcher</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">主要利用这些索引检索用户的查找关键词来产生查找结果。两者之间的接口是索引，所以除去索引部分，两者之间的耦合度很低。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Crawler</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Searcher</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">两部分尽量分开的目的主要是为了使两部分可以分布式配置在硬件平台上，例如将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Crawler</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Searcher</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">分别放在两个主机上，这样可以提升性能。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">你知道吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;a.</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，诞生了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">tika</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">gora</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">b. nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ivy</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">来进行依赖管理（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">之后）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">c. nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">是使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">svn</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行源代码管理的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">d. lucene</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，在搜索界相当有名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.&nbsp;ant</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">构建之后，生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">runtime</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">文件夹，该文件夹下面有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">deploy</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">local</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹，分别代表了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的两种运行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">方式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">f. nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">是通过什么连接起来的？通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">脚本。通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">命令把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">apache-nutch-1.6.job</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">提交给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;g.&nbsp;nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">入门重点在于分析</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">脚本文件。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8.5pt; font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: 240%; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-weight:normal\">2.Nutch</span></strong><strong><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">结构</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-weight:normal\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">构建完成之后生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;data</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹里有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;crawldb, linkdb segmentsf</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">抓取数据库，它包含了关于每一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Nutch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">已知的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的信息，包括它是否已经被获取，甚至是何时被获取的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">linkdb&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">：链接数据库，它包含了每一个已知</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的链接，包括源的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">以及链接的锚文本</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">segments</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">：一系列的分段，每一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">segments</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">都是一组被作为一个单元来获取的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">segments</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">是它本身这个目录以及它下面的子目录：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a.&nbsp;&nbsp;crawl_generate</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">：确定了将要被获取的一组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b. crawl_fetch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">包含了获取的每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的状态；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c.&nbsp;content</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">包含了从每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">获取回来的原始的内容；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d. &nbsp;parse_text</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">包含了每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解析以后的文本；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; e.&nbsp;parse_data</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">包含来自每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">被解析后内容中的外链和元数据；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f.&nbsp;crawl_parse</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">包含了外链的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，用来更新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">每爬一次都会生成一个文件夹，第一步由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">generator&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;crawl_generate</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，第二步</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawl_generate</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;content</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">存网页二进制源代码和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawl_fetch</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">存每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">url</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">抓取网页状态，第二步生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;crawl_parse</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">url</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的解析状态</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, parse_data</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">存页面源数据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,parse_text</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">存页面文本。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:2.3pt;margin-right:0cm;\r\nmargin-bottom:2.3pt;margin-left:0cm;text-align:center;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/1.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg (554&times;511)\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;text-align:center;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: 宋体;\">图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial;\">2.1<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">3.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">安装</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial;\">Nutch</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 24pt; font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a.</span><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: 宋体;\">没有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Arial;\">svn</span><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: 宋体;\">的装</span><span lang=\"