US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">什么是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">Hadoop<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的得名：这个名字是作者孩子给一个棕黄色的大象玩具命名的。作者的命名标准就是简短，容易发音和拼写，没有太多的意义，并且不会被用于别处。小孩子恰恰是这方面的高手。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apach</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">基金会下一个开源的分布式计算平台。以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分布式文件系统和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce(Google MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">开源实现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">为核心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">允许高容错性、高伸缩性，从而提供用户将分布式系统部署到低廉的硬件上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">编程模型允许用户在不了解系统底层细节的情况下开发。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的源头是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apach Nutch,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">始于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年。在我看来，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">用于完成至少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5TB</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">级别的数据运算和存储。</span></p>\r\n<h1><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">2.Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的概述</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">现在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoopnn</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">已经发展成为包含很多项目的集合。虽然核心是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">但相关的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Common</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Avro</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Chukwa</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hive</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">等项目也是不可或缺的。它们提供了互补或更高层次的服务。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop Common:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">及以前的版本中，包含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和其他项目公共内容，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">开始</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">被分离为独立的子项目，其余内容为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop Common</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS: Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分布式文件系统</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Distributed File System)&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">－</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;HDFS (Hadoop Distributed File System)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：并行计算框架，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">前使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;org.apache.hadoop.mapred&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">旧接口，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">版本开始引入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">API</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类似</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google BigTable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的分布式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NoSQL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">列数据库。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Avro</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">已经于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月成为顶级</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;Apache&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">项目）</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hive</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：数据仓库工具，由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">贡献。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Zookeeper</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：分布式锁设施，提供类似</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google Chubby</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的功能，由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Facebook</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">贡献。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Avro</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：新的数据序列化格式与传输工具，将逐步取代</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">原有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IPC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">机制。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Pig:</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大数据分析平台，为用户提供多种接口。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ambari</span><a name=\"ref_[6]_908354\"></a><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">管理工具，可以快捷的监控、部署、管理集群。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Sqoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：于在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HADOOP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">与传统的数据库间进行数据的传递。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">3.Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">与分布式开发</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分布式系统其实就是做分布式软件系统。包括分布式操作系统、分布式程序设计语言及其编译解释系统、分布式文件系统和分布式数据库系统。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是分布式软件系统中文件系统层的软件。它实现了分布式文件系统和部分分布式数据库系统的功能。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">模型的原理：利用一个输入的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key/value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对集合来产生一个输出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key/value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对集合。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">库的用户用两个函数来表达这个计算：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Map</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">用户自定义一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Map</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数接收输入的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key/value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对，然后产生一个中间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key/value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">对的集合。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">把所有具有相同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">value</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">集合到一起，然后传给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">用户自定义的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数接收</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">相关的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">集合。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">合并这些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">值。通常我们通过一个迭代器把中间的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">值提供给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数，从而处理无法全部放入内存的大量</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">value</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">值集合了。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">以下是具体原理：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">数据分布式存储</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分布式文件系统由一个名字结点和多个数据结点组成。每个结点都是一台普通的计算机。在使用方式上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">与我们熟悉的单机文件系统类似，利用它可以管理目录和文件，并且可以查看文件内容。但文件在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">底层被分割成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">block,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">block</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">被分散存储在不同的数据结点上，每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Block</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">还可以复制存储在其它数据结点上，达到高容错容灾的目的，而名字结点是整个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的核心，它记录每个文件被分成多少个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Block</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，在哪些数据结点里等重要信息。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分布式并行计算</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中有一个主控的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，用于调度和管理其它的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TaskTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTrackers</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以运行于集群中任意一台机器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TaskTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">负责执行任务，必须运行于名字结点上，也就是说名字结点既是存储结点，也是计算结点。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分配任务，如果一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TaskTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">出现问题，则把任务分给其它</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TaskTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">本地计算</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">数据存在哪台计算机，哪台计算机就进行计算，这样可以减少传输。在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这类基于集群的分布式系统中，计算结点可以很容易的任意扩充。这样就只用网络带宽是问题了，所以本地计算是个很好的解决办法。这也就是传说中的&ldquo;移动计算比移动数据更经济&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务粒度</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在把原始大数据切割时，通常让其小于或等于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Block</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">大小</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（默认</span><st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"m\" sourcevalue=\"64\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">64M</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这样能保证一个小数据集是在一台计算机上的，便于本地计算。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">数据分割</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Map</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务输出的中间结果按</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的范围划分成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务个数份，常用哈希函数，这样可以保证一定范围内的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是由一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">处理，从而简化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的过程。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">数据合并</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在数据分割之前，还可对中间数据进行合并。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Reduce</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Map</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务的中间结果在执行完合并和分割之后，以文件的形式存在本地的硬盘上，中间结果文件的位置会通知主控的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jobTracker,JobTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">再通知</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">去哪里取中间结果。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Map</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务产生的中间结果都是按照</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">值通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hash</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数划分。这些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">各自负责自己的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">区间，它们需要向其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">key</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">区间索要中间结果，然后继续执行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">函数，从而形成最终结果。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务管道</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有多少个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，就会有多少个最终结果，很多时候这些结果并不需要合并成一个最终结果，因为它们可以做另一个运算的输入，开始另外一个并行任务，这个时候，也就造成了任务管道。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">从三个角度将主机分为两种角色：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">最基本的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">master</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slaver</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. HDFS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">角度的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NameNode</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataNode</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。在分布式的文件系统中，文件目录管理很重要，管理目录相关于主人。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的角度，将主机分为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TeskTracker</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">job</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可以被分为多个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">task,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">所以&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可分为三种安装模式：单机、伪分布式、分布式模式，顾名思义。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">4.HBase</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的数据管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是一个分布式的、面向列的开源数据库，该技术来源于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Chang et al</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">所撰写的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">论文</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;Bigtable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：一个结构化数据的分布式存储系统</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。就像</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bigtable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">利用了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">文件系统（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">File System</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）所提供的分布式数据存储一样，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之上提供了类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bigtable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Apache</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">项目的子项目。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不同于一般的关系数据库，它是一个适合于非结构化数据存储的数据库。另一个不同的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">基于列的而不是基于行的模式。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">三大组成部分：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBaseMaster</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">主</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://product.it168.com/list/b/0402_1.shtml\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"服务器\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;\r\ntext-underline:none\">服务器</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bigtable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的主</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://product.pcpop.com/Server/10734_1.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"服务器\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;\r\ntext-underline:none\">服务器</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">类似。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HRegionServer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">域服务器，与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bigtable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tablet</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">服务器类似。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBaseClient</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HBase</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">客户端是由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">org.apache.hadoop.HBase.client.HTable</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">定义的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-indent:21.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h1><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\">5.Hive</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的数据管理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:240%\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">hive</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是基于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的一个数据仓库工具，可以将结构化的数据文件映射为一张数据库表，并提供完整的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sql</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">查询功能，可以将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sql</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">语句转换为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">任务进行运行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">其优点是学习成本低，可以通过类</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SQL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">语句快速实现简单的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">统计，不必开发专门的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">应用，十分适合数据仓库的统计分析。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-10-24 15:27:05'),(22,26,'Hadoop入门2 基于Linux配置Hadoop集群','<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">从三个角度将主机分为两种角色：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1. </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">最基本的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slaver</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. HDFS</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">角度的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NameNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">。在分布式的文件系统中，文件目录管理很重要，管理目录相关于主人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. MapReduce</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">的角度，将主机分为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TeskTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">。一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">job</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">可以被分为多个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">task,</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">所以&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">可分为三种安装模式：单机、伪分布式、分布式模式，顾名思义。为了方便演示，这里搭建一个只有三台主机的小集群。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">三台机子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ip</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">要能相互</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ping</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">通，这个就不说了。以下是三台机子的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和分工。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">x.x.x.141 - Master,Namenode,JobTracker -sivc101</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">x.x.x.143 - Slave,DataNode,TaskTracker&nbsp; -sivc102</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">x.x.x.144 &ndash; Slave,SataNode,TaskTracker &ndash; sivc103 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">三个节点上均是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CentOS</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">系统，并且有一个相同的用户</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc</span></b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器主要配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NameNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的角色，负责总管分布式数据和分解任务的执行；两个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salve</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TaskTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的角色，负责分布式数据存储以及任务的执行。其实应该还应该有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器，用来作为</span><b>备用</b>，如果<span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器</span><b>宕机</b>，还有备用可以马上启用。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">这些基础准备好之后下面就开始配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">环境了，前四节是配置，第五节是常见错误解析，第六节针对配置过程中用到的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">linux</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">语法进行详解。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">1. </span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">JDK<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">此处省略一万字。</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">2. </span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置主机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">IP</span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和主机名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/hosts</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下添加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hosts</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">信息，用于定义主机名和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">关系</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">127.0.0.1&nbsp; localhost<br />\r\nx.x.x.141&nbsp; sivc101<br />\r\nx.x.x.143&nbsp; sivc102<br />\r\nx.x.x.144&nbsp; sivc103</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Consolas; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/hostname</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下添加主机名：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">然后就可以通过主机名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ping</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">能各个主机</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">PING</span></st1:place><span lang=\"EN-US\"> sivc101 (xx.xx.xx.141) 56(84) bytes of data.<br />\r\n64 bytes from sivc101 (xxx.xxx.xxx.141): icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=0.106 ms<br />\r\n64 bytes from sivc101 (xxx.xxx.xxx.141): icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=0.095 ms</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">3. </span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置免密码</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">SSH<o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">省去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">sudo </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">yum apt-get install ssh</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">&hellip;&hellip;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">运行过程中需要管理远端</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">守护进程，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">启动以后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">NameNode</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">是通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SSH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Secure Shell</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">）来启动和停止各个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">DataNode</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">上的各种守护进程的。这就必须在节点之间执行指令的时候是不需要输入密码的形式，故我们需要配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SSH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">运用无密码公钥认证的形式，这样</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">NameNode</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SSH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">无密码登录并启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">DataName</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">进程，同样原理，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">DataNode</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">上也能使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">SSH</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">无密码登录到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">NameNode</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">节点上执行以下命令：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ssh-keygen -t rsa -P </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">接着在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">Master</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">节点上做如下配置，把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">id_rsa.pub</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">追加到授权的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">key</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">里面去</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Verdana; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在验证前，需要做两件事儿。第一件事儿是修改文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">权限（权限的设置非常重要，因为不安全的设置安全设置，会让你不能使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">RSA</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">功能），另一件事儿是用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">root</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">用户设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/ssh/sshd_config&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的内容。使其无密码登录有效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1）<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">修改文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; chmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">root</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">用户登录服务器修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/ssh/sshd_config&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的下列内容。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; RSAAuthentication yes # </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">启用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> RSA </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">认证</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PubkeyAuthentication yes # </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">启用公钥私钥配对认证方式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AuthorizedKeysFile .ssh/authorized_keys # </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">公钥文件路径（和上面生成的文件同）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">设置完之后记得重启</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务，才能使刚才设置有效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; service sshd restart</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">退出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">root</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">登录，使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">普通用户验证是否成功。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ssh localhost</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/14.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">从上图中得知无密码登录本级已经设置完毕，接下来的事儿是把公钥复制所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器上。使用下面的命令格式进行复制公钥：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">scp ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">远程用户名</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">@</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">远程服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP:~/</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下面就针对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;x.x.35.146&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的身为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slave </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的节点进行配置。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">上的公钥复制到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/15.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">从上图中我们得知，已经把文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;id_rsa.pub&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">传过去了，因为并没有建立起无密码连接，所以在连接时，仍然要提示输入输入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的密码。为了确保确实已经把文件传过去了，查看是否存在这个文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　从上面得知我们已经成功把公钥复制过去了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/home/sivc/&quot;</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh&quot;</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">这一步并不是必须的，如果在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/home/sivc&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">已经存在就不需要创建了，因为我们之前并没有对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器做过无密码登录配置，所以该文件是不存在的。用下面命令进行创建。（备注：用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">登录系统，如果不涉及系统文件修改，一般情况下都是用我们之前建立的普通用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行执行命令。）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">mkdir ~/.ssh</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">然后是修改文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的用户权限，把他的权限修改为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;700&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，用下面命令执行：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">chmod 700 ~/.ssh</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">备注：如果不进行，即使你按照前面的操作设置了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">权限，并配置了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/ssh/sshd_config&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，还重启了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sshd</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">能用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;ssh localhost&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行无密码登录，但是对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行登录仍然需要输入密码，就是因为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹的权限设置不对。这个文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码登录时系统自动生成时，权限自动为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;700&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">，如果是自己手动创建，它的组权限和其他权限都有，这样就会导致</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">RSA</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码远程登录失败。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）追加到授权文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">到目前为止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的公钥也有了，文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">也有了，且权限也修改了。这一步就是把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的公钥追加到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的授权文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中去。使用下面命令进行追加并修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;authorized_keys&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件权限：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">cat ~/id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; ~/.ssh/authorized_keys<br />\r\nchmod 600 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">root</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">用户修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/ssh/sshd_config&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">具体步骤参考前面</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，具体分为两步：第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">是修改配置文件；第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">是重启</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码登录</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc102<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">当前面的步骤设置完毕，就可以使用下面命令格式进行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码登录了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">ssh </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">远程服务器</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">最后记得把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/home/hadoop/&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">目录下的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;id_rsa.pub&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件删除掉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">rm &ndash;r ~/id_rsa.pub</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">到此为止，我们经过前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">步已经实现了从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;Master.Hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;Slave1.Hadoop&quot;SSH</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码登录，下面就是重复上面的步骤把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc103</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器进行配置。这样，我们就完成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">无密码登录所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">4. Hadoop</span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">集群安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所有的机器上都要安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">，现在就先在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">Master</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">服务器安装，然后其他服务器按照步骤重复进行即可。安装和配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">需要以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&quot;</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:red\">root</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">的身份进行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">4.1 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop<o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　首先用</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:red\">root</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nVerdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">用户登录</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">sivc101</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">机器，把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">解压到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">opt</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">目录。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下一步进入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/opt&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">目录下，用下面命令把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop-<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\">1.0.0</st1:chsdate>.tar.gz&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行解压，并将其命名为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，把该文件夹的读权限分配给普通用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，然后删除</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop-1.0.0.tar.gz&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">安装包。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">最后把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的安装路径添加到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/profile&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中，修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/profile&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件（配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">环境变量的文件），将以下语句添加到末尾，并使其有效：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"># set hadoop path<br />\r\nexport HADOOP_HOME=/opt/hadoop<br />\r\nexport PATH=$PATH :$HADOOP_HOME/bin</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/opt/hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;tmp&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">mkdir /opt/hadoop/tmp</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">重启</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/profile&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">source /etc/profile<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">4.2 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop<o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop-env.sh<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">该</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop-env.sh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件位于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/opt/hadoop/conf&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">目录下。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在文件的末尾添加下面内容。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"># set java environment<br />\r\nexport JAVA_HOME=/opt/java/jdk<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\">1.6.0</st1:chsdate>_31<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">core-site.xml</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Hadoop</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">核心配置文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">core-site.xml</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">，这里配置的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">HDFS</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">的地址和端口号。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><configuration><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<property><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <name>hadoop.tmp.dir</name><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <value>/opt/hadoop/tmp</value><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </property>\r\n</configuration></span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">（</span><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">备注：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">请先在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> /opt/hadoop </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">目录下建立</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\"> tmp </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">文件夹）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <description>A base for other temporary directories.</description><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n<!-- file system properties --><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<property><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <name>fs.default.name</name><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <value>hdfs://</value></property>\r\n</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#333333\">192.168.1.2</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">:</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#333333\">9000</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">备注：如没有配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop.tmp.dir</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">参数，此时系统默认的临时目录为：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/tmp/hadoo-hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。而这个目录在每次重启后都会被干掉，必须重新执行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">format</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">才行，否则会出错。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.05pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#3366FF\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hdfs-site.xml</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的配置，配置的备份方式默认为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><configuration><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<property><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <name>dfs.replication</name><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <value></value></property>\r\n</configuration></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#333333\">1</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (</span><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">备注：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">replication </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">是数据副本数量，默认为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">salve</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">少于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">台就会报错</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n<configuration><o:p></o:p></configuration></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">mapred-site.xml</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">文件</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">MapReduce</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的配置文件，配置的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JobTracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的地址和端口。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><configuration><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<property><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <name>mapred.job.tracker</name><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <value>http://</value></property>\r\n</configuration></span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#333333\">192.168.1.2</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">:</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:#333333\">9001</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">masters</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">有两种方案：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）第一种</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">localhost</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sivc101</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）第二种</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">去掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，加入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x.x.x.141</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">为保险起见，启用第二种，因为万一忘记配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/hosts&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">局域网的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DNS</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">失效，这样就会出现意想不到的错误，但是一旦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配对，网络畅通，就能通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">找到相应主机。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slaves</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">主机特有）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">有两种方案：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）第一种</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">去掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，每行只添加一个主机名，把剩余的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">主机名都填上。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">sivc101<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">sivc102<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">sivc103<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">）第二种</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">去掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">，加入集群中所有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Slave</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">机器的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">IP</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">，也是每行一个。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">现在在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器上的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">配置就结束了，剩下的就是配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器上的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">一种方式是按照上面的步骤，把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的安装包在用普通用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;scp&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">复制到其他机器的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/home/hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">目录下，然后根据实际情况进行安装配置，除了第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">步，那是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">特有的。用下面命令格式进行。（备注：此时切换到普通用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">scp ~/hadoop-<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\">1.0.0</st1:chsdate>.tar.gz hadoop@</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP:~/</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">另一种方式是将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">上配置好的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">所在文件夹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/opt/hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">复制到所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/opt&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">目录下（实际上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">机器上的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slavers</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件是不必要的，</span> <span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">复制了也没问题）。用下面命令格式进行。（备注：此时用户可以为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">也可以为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">root</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">scp&nbsp;-r&nbsp;/opt/hadoop&nbsp;root@</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IP:/usr/</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">4.3 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">启动及验证<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）格式化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件系统</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;Master.Hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">上使用普通用户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">进行操作。（备注：只需一次，下次启动不再需要格式化，只需</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> start-all.sh</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop namenode -format</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在启动前关闭集群中所有机器的防火墙，不然会出现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">开后又自动关闭。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">service iptables stop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">使用下面命令启动。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">start-all.sh</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">执行结果如下：</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">可以通过以下启动日志看出，首先启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namenode </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">接着启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，然后启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">secondarynamenode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">。再启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jobtracker</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">，然后启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">tasktracker1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">tasktracker2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">成功后，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Master </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> tmp </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹中生成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> dfs </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中的</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">tmp </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹中均生成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> dfs </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> mapred </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）验证</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）验证方法一：用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;jps&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">命令</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">上用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> java</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">自带的小工具</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jps</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">查看进程。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">上用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jps</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">查看进程。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/20.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">发现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">没有启动起来，查看日至信息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent: 21pt; text-align: center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/21.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">通过分析，日志提示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NameNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">不一致。原因是两次或以上格式化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NameNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，关于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">不同的解决办法在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中讲解。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">）验证方式二：用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&quot;hadoop dfsadmin -report&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">用这个命令可以查看</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">集群的状态。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">还可以通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50070</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50030</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">端口查看集群状态，如：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://202.189.141.141:50070/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://202.189.141.141:50070</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">5. </span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">问题解决</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">5.1 namespaceID</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">不一致<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">a. </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">第一种解决方案如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）先删除</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/usr/hadoop/tmp&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;rm -rf /usr/hadoop/tmp</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/usr/hadoop/tmp&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件夹</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;mkdir /usr/hadoop/tmp</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）删除</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/tmp&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">下以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">开头文件</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;rm -rf /tmp/hadoop*</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）重新格式化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;hadoop namenode -format</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;start-all.sh</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">使用第一种方案，有种不好处就是原来集群上的重要数据全没有了。假如说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">集群已经运行了一段时间。建议采用第二种。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">第二种方案如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）修改每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">使其与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">一致。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">或者</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">）修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">使其与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">一致。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">该</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">slave</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;namespaceID&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">位于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot; /hadoop/tmp/dfs/data/current/VERSION&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件中，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">master</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的位于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot; /hadoop/tmp/dfs/name/current/VERSION&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.2 HADOOP_HOME is deprecated<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoo<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\">p 1.0.0</st1:chsdate></span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">版本，安装完之后敲入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">命令时，<b>老</b>是提示这个警告：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Warning: $HADOOP_HOME is deprecated.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">经查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop-<st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\">1.0.0</st1:chsdate>/bin/hadoop</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">脚本和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop-config.sh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">脚本，发现脚本中对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HADOOP_HOME</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的环境变量设置做了判断，笔者的环境根本不需要设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HADOOP_HOME</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">环境变量。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案一：编辑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/profile&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件，去掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HADOOP_HOME</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的变量设定，重新输入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop fs</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">命令，警告消失。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案二：编辑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/profile&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件，添加一个环境变量，之后警告消失：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">export HADOOP_HOME_WARN_SUPPRESS=1</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案三：编辑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;hadoop-config.sh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件，把下面的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;if - fi&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">功能注释掉。</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.3 Slave</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">服务器中<span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode</span>启动后又自动关闭<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">查看日志发下如下错误。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">　</span></b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ERROR&nbsp;org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.server.datanode.DataNode: java.io.IOException: Call to ... failed on local exception: java.net.NoRouteToHostException:&nbsp;No route to host</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案是：关闭防火墙</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">service iptables stop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.4 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">从本地往<span lang=\"EN-US\">hdfs</span>文件系统上传文件<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">出现如下错误：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">INFO hdfs.DFSClient: Exception in createBlockOutputStream java.io.IOException:&nbsp;<b>Bad connect ack with firstBadLink</b><br />\r\n</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">INFO hdfs.DFSClient: Abandoning block blk_-1300529705803292651_37023<br />\r\n</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">WARN hdfs.DFSClient: DataStreamer Exception: java.io.IOException:&nbsp;<b>Unable to create new block.</b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案是：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）关闭防火墙</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">service iptables stop</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）禁用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">selinux</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">编辑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &quot;<b>/etc/selinux/config</b>&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">文件，设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;<b>SELINUX</b>=<b>disabled</b>&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.5 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">安全模式导致的错误<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:19.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">出现如下错误：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">or</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">g.apache.hadoop.dfs.SafeModeException:&nbsp;<b>Cannot delete ..., Name node is in safe mode</b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">在分布式文件系统启动的时候，开始的时候会有安全模式，当分布式文件系统处于安全模式的情况下，文件系统中的内容不允许修改也不允许删除，直到安全模式结束。安全模式主要是为了系统启动的时候检查各个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DataNode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">上数据块的有效性，同时根据策略必要的复制或者删除部分数据块。运行期通过命令也可以进入安全模式。在实践过程中，系统启动的时候去修改和删除文件也会有安全模式不允许修改的出错提示，只需要等待一会儿即可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案是：关闭安全模式</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop dfsadmin -safemode leave</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.6 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">解决<span lang=\"EN-US\">Exceeded MAX_FAILED_UNIQUE_FETCHES<o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">出现错误如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Shuffle Error: Exceeded MAX_FAILED_UNIQUE_FETCHES; bailing-out</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">程序里面需要打开多个文件，进行分析，系统一般默认数量是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1024</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，（用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ulimit -a</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">可以看到）对于正常使用是够了，但是对于程序来讲，就太少了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案是：修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">个文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/security/limits.conf&quot;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">vim /etc/security/limits.conf</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">加上：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">soft nofile 102400<br />\r\nhard nofile 409600</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/pam.d/login&quot;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">vim /etc/pam.d/login</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">添加：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">session required /lib/security/pam_limits.so</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">针对第一个问题我纠正下答案：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">这是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">reduce</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">预处理阶段</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">shuffle</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">时获取已完成的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的输出失败次数超过上限造成的，上限默认为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。引起此问题的方式可能会有很多种，比如网络连接不正常，连接超时，带宽较差以及端口阻塞等。通常框架内网络情况较好是不会出现此错误的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.7 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">解决<span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;Too many fetch-failures&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">出现这个问题主要是结点间的连通不够全面。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案是：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）检查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;/etc/hosts&quot;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">要求本机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ip </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">对应</span> <span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">服务器名</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">要求要包含所有的服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ip +</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">服务器名</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></b><b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">）检查</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;.ssh/authorized_keys&quot;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">要求包含所有服务器（包括其自身）的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">public key</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.8 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">处理速度特别的慢<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">出现</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span></b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">很<b>快</b>，但是</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">reduce</span></b><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">很<b>慢</b>，而且反复出现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;<b>reduce=0%</b>&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">结合解决方案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.7</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，然后修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;conf/hadoop-env.sh&quot;</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&quot;export HADOOP_HEAPSIZE =4000&quot;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.9</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt\">解决<span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop OutOfMemoryError</span>问题<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nVerdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　出现这种异常，明显是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">内存不够得原因。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案如下：要修改所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">内存大小。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Java &ndash;Xms <st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"1024\" unitname=\"m\">1024m</st1:chmetcnv> -Xmx <st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"4096\" unitname=\"m\">4096m</st1:chmetcnv></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">一般</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">的最大内存使用应该为总内存大小的一半，我们使用的</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"8\" unitname=\"g\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8G</span></st1:chmetcnv><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">内存，所以设置为</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\"on\" tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"4096\" unitname=\"m\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4096m</span></st1:chmetcnv><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">，这一值可能依旧不是最优的值。</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.10 Namenode in safe mode<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">bin/hadoop dfsadmin -safemode leave</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.11 IO</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">写操作出现问题<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">0-1246359584298, infoPort=50075, ipcPort=50020):Got exception while serving blk_-5911099437886836280_1292 to /172.16.100.165:<br />\r\njava.net.SocketTimeoutException: 480000 millis timeout while waiting for channel to be ready for write. ch : java.nio.channels.SocketChannel[connected local=/<br />\r\n172.16.100.165:50010 remote=/172.16.100.165:50930]<br />\r\n</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">at org.apache.hadoop.net.SocketIOWithTimeout.waitForIO(SocketIOWithTimeout.java:185)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; at rg.apache.hadoop.SocketOutputStream.waitForWritable(SocketOutputStream.java:159)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &hellip;<br />\r\n</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">It seems there are many reasons that it can timeout, the example given in HADOOP-3831 is a slow reading client.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop-site.xml</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\">中设置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">dfs.datanode.socket.write.timeout=0</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">5.12 status of 255 error<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">错误类型：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java.io.IOException: Task process exit with nonzero status of 255.<br />\r\n</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">at org.apache.hadoop.mapred.TaskRunner.run(TaskRunner.java:424)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">错误原因：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Set mapred.jobtracker.retirejob.interval and mapred.userlog.retain.hours to higher value. By default, their values are 24 hours. These might be the reason for failure, though I\'m not sure restart.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">解决方案如下：单个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">如果一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">datanode </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">出现问题，解决之后需要重新加入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">cluster</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">而不重启</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">cluster</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">，方法如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">bin/hadoop-daemon.sh start datanode<br />\r\nbin/hadoop-daemon.sh start jobtracker</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"background:red\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">6</span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">．用到的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\">Linux</span><span microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">命令</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" microsoft=\"\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n13.5pt;line-height:240%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">6.1 chmod</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">命令详解<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　使用权限：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所有使用者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　使用方式：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod [-cfvR] [--help] [--version] mode file...<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　说明：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Linux/Unix </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">的档案存取权限分为三级</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">档案拥有者、群组、其他。利用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> chmod </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">可以藉以控制档案如何被他人所存取。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">mode </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">：权限设定字串，格式如下</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">[ugoa...][[+-=][rwxX]...][,...]</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">，其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">u </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">表示该档案的拥有者，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">g </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">表示与该档案的拥有者属于同一个群体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(group)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">者，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">o </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">表示其他以外的人，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">a </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">表示这三者皆是。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">+ </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示增加权限、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">- </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示取消权限、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">= </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示唯一设定权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\nr </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示可读取，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">w </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示可写入，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">x </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示可执行，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">X </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">表示只有当该档案是个子目录或者该档案已经被设定过为可执行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n-c : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">若该档案权限确实已经更改，才显示其更改动作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n-f : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">若该档案权限无法被更改也不要显示错误讯息</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n-v : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">显示权限变更的详细资料</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n-R : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">对目前目录下的所有档案与子目录进行相同的权限变更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">即以递回的方式逐个变更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)<br />\r\n--help : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">显示辅助说明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n--version : </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">显示版本</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　范例：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将档案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> file1.txt </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">设为所有人皆可读取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">chmod ugo+r file1.txt</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将档案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> file1.txt </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">设为所有人皆可读取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod a+r file1.txt<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将档案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> file1.txt </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> file2.txt </span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">设为该档案拥有者，与其所属同一个群体者可写入，但其他以外的人则不可写入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod ug+w,o-w file1.txt file2.txt<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> ex1.py </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">设定为只有该档案拥有者可以执行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">chmod</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> u+x ex1.py<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将目前目录下的所有档案与子目录皆设为任何人可读取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"background:#D9D9D9\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">chmod</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> -R a+r *<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　此外</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">也可以用数字来表示权限如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> chmod 777 file<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　语法为：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod abc file<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　其中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">a,b,c</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">各为一个数字，分别表示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">User</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Group</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">、及</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Other</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">的权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">r=4</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">w=2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">x=1<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　若要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">rwx</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">属性则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">4+2+1=7</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　若要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">rw-</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">属性则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">4+2=6</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　若要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">r-x</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">属性则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">4+1=7</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　范例：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod a=rwx file </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> chmod 777 file </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">效果相同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod ug=rwx,o=x file </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> chmod 771 file </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">效果相同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　若用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chmod 4755 filename</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">可使此程式具有</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:fuchsia\">root</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nVerdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">的权限</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">6.2 chown</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">命令详解<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　使用权限：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">root<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　使用方式：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chown [-cfhvR] [--help] [--version] user[:group] file...<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　说明：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">Linux/Unix </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">是多人多工作业系统，所有的档案皆有拥有者。利用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> chown </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">可以将档案的拥有者加以改变。一般来说，这个指令只有是由系统管理者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(root)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所使用，一般使用者没有权限可以改变别人的档案拥有者，也没有权限可以自己的档案拥有者改设为别人。只有系统管理者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(root)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">才有这样的权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">user : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">新的档案拥有者的使用者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">IDgroup : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">新的档案拥有者的使用者群体</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(group)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-c : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">若该档案拥有者确实已经更改，才显示其更改动作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-f : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">若该档案拥有者无法被更改也不要显示错误讯息</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-h : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">只对于连结</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(link)</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">进行变更，而非该</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> link </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">真正指向的档案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-v : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">显示拥有者变更的详细资料</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-R : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">对目前目录下的所有档案与子目录进行相同的拥有者变更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">即以递回的方式逐个变更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">--help : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">显示辅助说明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">--version : </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">显示版本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:blue\">　　范例：</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将档案</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> file1.txt </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">的拥有者设为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> users </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">群体的使用者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> jessie<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chown jessie:users file1.txt<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　将目前目录下的所有档案与子目录的拥有者皆设为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> users </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">群体的使用者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"> lamport<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">chown -R lamport:users *<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rw------- (600) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">只有属主有读写权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rw-r--r-- (644) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">只有属主有读写权限；而属组用户和其他用户只有读权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rwx------ (700) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">只有属主有读、写、执行权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rwxr-xr-x (755) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">属主有读、写、执行权限；而属组用户和其他用户只有读、执行权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rwx--x--x (711) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">属主有读、写、执行权限；而属组用户和其他用户只有执行权限。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rw-rw-rw- (666) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所有用户都有文件读、写权限。这种做法不可取。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">-rwxrwxrwx (777) -- </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所有用户都有读、写、执行权限。更不可取的做法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　以下是对目录的两个普通设定：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">drwx------ (700) - </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">只有属主可在目录中读、写。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">drwxr-xr-x (755) - </span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">所有用户可读该目录，但只有属主才能改变目录中的内容</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o