pan><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">个指定了用户名，命令执行后需要输入用户密码；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">个没有指定用户名，命令执行后需要输入用户名和密码；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:red\">　</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#3366FF\">　　</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:#3366FF\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#3366FF\">）从远程服务器复制到本地服务器</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">　　从远程复制到本地的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">scp</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">命令与上面的命令雷同，只要将从本地复制到远程的命令后面</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nVerdana;color:#333333\">个参数互换顺序就行了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 17pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:Verdana;color:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-10-25 15:48:36'),(24,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2013-10-28 21:35:39'),(26,24,'Nutch入门教程二 功能流程','<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">的功能流程可大致分为爬虫，索引，搜索，分析四大块。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><!--[endif]--></span><!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<h1><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%\">1. </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">爬虫</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 25.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 25.2pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Helvetica;\">generate -&gt; fetch -&gt; parse -&gt;updatedb </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">（爬虫）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Helvetica;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;-&gt;invertLinks (</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">索引</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Helvetica;\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">其工作策略一般则可以分为累积式抓取（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">cumulative crawling</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">）和增量式抓取（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">incremental crawling</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">）两种。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">累积式抓取是指从某一个时间点开始，通过遍历的方式抓取系统所能允许存储和处理的所有网页。在理想的软硬件环境下，经过足够的运行时间，累积式抓取的策略可以保证抓取到相当规模的网页集合。但由于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Web</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据的动态特性，集合中网页的被抓取时间点是不同的，页面被更新的情况也不同，因此累积式抓取到的网页集合事实上并无法与真实环境中的网络数据保持一致。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">与累积式抓取不同，增量式抓取是指在具有一定量规模的网络页面集合的基础上，采用更新数据的方式选取已有集合中的过时网页进行抓取，以保证所抓取到的数据与真实网络数据足够接近。进行增量式抓取的前提是，系统已经抓取了足够数量的网络页面，并具有这些页面被抓取的时间信息。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">面向实际应用环境的网络蜘蛛设计中，通常既包括累积式抓取，也包括增量式抓取的策略。累积式抓取一般用于数据集合的整体建立或大规模更新阶段；而增量式抓取则主要针对数据集合的日常维护与即时更新。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在确定了抓取策略之后，如何从充分利用网络带宽，合理确定网页数据更新的时间点就成了网络蜘蛛运行策略中的核心问题。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">总体而言，在合理利用软硬件资源进行针对网络数据的即时抓取方面，已经形成了相对比较成熟的技术和实用性解决方案，这方面目前所需解决的主要问题，是如何更好的处理动态网络数据问题以及更好的根据网页质量修正抓取策略的问题。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 25.2pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Helvetica;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">a. inject,</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">首先注入抓取初始地址。 </span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">inject</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作主要作用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">集合进行格式化和过滤，消除其中的非法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，并设定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">状态</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(unfetched),&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">按照一定方法进行初始化分值；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">进行合并，消除重复的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">入口；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">及其状态、分值存入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据库，与原数据库中重复的则删除旧的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">更</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">换新的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">inject</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作结果：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据库内容得到更新，包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">及其状态。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">语法：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#D9D9D9\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; nutch inject data/crawldb urls</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如果是首次操作，会创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">data</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹，和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">截图：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 25.5pt; line-height: 25.2pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 25.5pt; line-height: 25.2pt; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<h2><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">b. Generate</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">，产生抓取列表<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"Default\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">generate</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作主要作用：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据库中将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">取出并进行过滤</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">进行排序，通过域名、链接数和一种</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hash</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">算法综合进行降序排列</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=