d-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">d.Parse, </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">解析网页内容</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-weight:normal\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">parse</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作主要作用：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">解析</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">segment</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">fetch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">得到的页面，并进行整理，将页面分成为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">parse-date</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; parse-text </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; parse-date</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中保存的是页面的题名、作者、日期、链接等内容</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; parse-text</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中保存的是页面的文本内容</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">parse</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作结果：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">fetch</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">得到的页面解析为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">text</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">data</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，存于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">segment</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">目录下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">语法：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#D9D9D9\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bin/nutch parse data/segments/20131027214114/</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">截图：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; parse</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">之后，如流程图，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/data/segments/*/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中多了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawl_parse ,parse_data </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">parse_text</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h2><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体\">e. update</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体\">，更新<span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span></span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-weight:normal\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">updatedb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作主要作用：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">根据</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">segment</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">目录下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">fetch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">parse</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹中的内容，对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">进行更新，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">增加新的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，更换旧的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">updatedb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作结果：更新了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据库，为下一轮抓取做准备。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">语法：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#D9D9D9\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bin/nutch updatedb data/crawldb &ndash;dir data/segments</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">截图：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">状态：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">更新完之后一次完整的抓取结束，查看现在的抓取数据：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#D9D9D9\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bin/nutch&nbsp;&nbsp;readdb&nbsp;&nbsp;data/crawldb&nbsp;&nbsp;-stats</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h1><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%\">2. </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">索引（</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">InvertLinks</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:240%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">）</span></strong><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:240%;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">invertlinks</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作用来更新</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Linkdb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">数据库，为索引做准备，不是主要操作。而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">index</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作包括了以下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">个主要操作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">invertlinks</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作主要作用：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">转换成文本，在索引数据之前，首先必须将数据转换成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">能够处理的格式，纯文本字符流。但是在现实世界中，信息多以富媒体文档呈现：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PDF, WORD, EXCEL, HTML, XML</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">等。为此，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">采用了插件机制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(plugin)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，通过各种各样的文档解析器，将富媒体转换成纯文字字符流。文档解析器种类繁多，开发人员可以根据需要进行选择，同时还可以自己修改或编写，非常灵活方便。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">分析，在对数据进行索引前，还要进行预处理，对数据进行分析使之更加适合被索引。分析数据时，先将文本数据切分成一些大块或者语汇单元（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">tokens)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，然后对它们执行一些可选的操作，例如：在索引之前将这些语汇单元转换成小写，使得搜索对大小写不敏感；最有代表性的是要从输入中去掉一些使用很频繁但却没有实际意义的词，比如英文文本中的一些停止词</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(a</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">an</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">the</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">in</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">on</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。同样的，我们也需要分析输入的语汇单元，以便从词语中去掉一些不必要的字母以找到它们的词干。这一处理过程称为分析</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(analyze)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。分析技术在索引和搜索时都会用到。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将分析后的数据写入索引，对输入数据分析处理完之后，就可以将结果写入索引文件中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">采用的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">lucene</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的索引格式，故我将介绍一下这种称为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">倒排索引</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的索引结构。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">截图：</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">反转链接在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">data</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹中会多出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">linkdb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这个文件夹</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">什么是倒排索引？</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lucene</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将输入数据以一种称为倒排索引的数据结构进行存储。倒排索引源于实际应用中需要根据属性的值来查找记录。这种索引表中的每一项都包括一个属性值和具有该属性值的各记录的地址。由于不是由记录来确定属性值，而是由属性值来确定记录的位置，因而称为倒排索引。在进行关键字快速查找时，这种数据结构能够有效的利用磁盘空间。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lucene</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会使用倒排结构存储数据的原因是：把从文档中抽取出来的语汇单元看作是查找关键字，而不是把文档作为中心实体。换句话说，倒排索引不是回答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这个文档中包含哪些单词？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这个问题，而是经过优化以后用来快速回答</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">哪些文档包含单词</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">X</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这个问题。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-10-28 21:40:19'),(27,24,'Nutch入门教程三 整合Solr4.5','<p>&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">基本的功能能跑之后就是解决页面索引问题，因为学习</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">本来就是为了抓淘宝的数据，而且我喜欢遇到问题再去解决，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">再强也只是一个框架，在我看来没必要花太多时间去学怎么用它。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Solr</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">是一个独立的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/4173560.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">企业级搜索</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">应用服务器，它对外提供类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Web-service</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">API</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">接口。用户可以通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">http</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">请求，向搜索引擎服务器提交一定格式的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">XML</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件，生成索引。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 39.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">首先安装</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Solr4.5</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Solr.apache.com</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">下找到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Resources-&gt;version Control-&gt;tags-&gt;4.5, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">然后直接通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">svn checkout</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">到本地。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">svn co <a href=\"http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucence/dev/\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lucence/dev/</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">复制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">conf</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">目录中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">schema-solr4.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr/collection1/conf</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">目录，改名为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">schema.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，覆盖原来文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">修改</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr/collection1/conf/schema.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><fields></fields></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">下增加：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><field name=\"_version_\" type=\"long\" indexed=\"true\" stored=\"true\"></field>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">然后在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">example</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件夹内启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">java &ndash;jar start.jar<o:p></o:p></