amily:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">替换为</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">tokenizer class=&quot;com.chenlb.mmseg4j.solr.MMSegTokenizerFactory&quot;mode=&quot;complex&quot;/&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><tokenizer class=\"com.chenlb.mmseg4j.solr.MMSegTokenizerFactory\" mode=\"complex\"></tokenizer><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">提交索引</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> solrindex</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">方法将索引提交给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">服务器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">前期已经使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">爬过淘宝</span><st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"3\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3c</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">类，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">depth</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。将</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">data</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">提交给</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">nutch solrindex http://localhost:<a href=\"http://host2:8983/solr\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:\r\nnone\">8983/solr</span></a>&nbsp; data/crawldb -linkdb data/linkdb -dir data/ segments</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">之后即可在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">http://localhost:<a href=\"http://host2:8983/solr\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:windowtext;\r\ntext-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">8983/solr</span></a>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中看到结果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/23.jpg\" alt=\"23.jpg (901&times;577)\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">管理页面进行相关配置</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-10-29 21:58:00'),(28,29,'2013/06 大二暑假 事情发生之后都会显得云淡风轻','<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">我刻意的把一堆事情做完之后才写这个总结。那些重要的事、不得不做的事已经结束了，我打算给自己两天时间大睡一觉，回家之后发现可能事情还没有让我累到可以给自己放假的程度，毕竟已经过去了，当时的紧张和忙碌的准备都已经感受不到，剩下的唯有更广阔的视野和从零开始的勇气。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">首先应该说的是大二的考试。在开学前总是立志做个学霸后来也都不了了之。数据结构和英语什么的在最后一个星期预习之后也都是<span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span>分左右。不喜欢的软件工程也还是逃不了<span lang=\"EN-US\">60+</span>的命运，其实还好，总体给自己打<span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span>分。依然，大三再不尝试学霸就没机会了，共勉。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">其次是蓝桥杯，在我看来运气是大部分，加上比赛第<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>届还是比较简单，拿了河南省一等奖，北京之行也是打了酱油弄一个三等奖。毕竟我也没在算法上太花力气，但是现在看来我的工程能力已经足够了，接下来的时间完全可以拿出大部分时间做做算法，了解了解<span lang=\"EN-US\">hack</span>文化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总之暑假开始了，我依然特别特别幸福，<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>天假期之后是苏州高博的<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>周实训。这一定是个幸福的<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>天。加油吧。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以下是学习总结：<sp