"font-family:宋体\">XML:<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8991206\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8991206</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">card trick::<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8988921\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8988921</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">画直线算法：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9039267\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9039267</a><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</p>','2013-07-14 13:48:27'),(29,28,'2013/5/27 大二下第13周 算法重点','<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 16pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">上周总结：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">javaWeb</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">学习中，了解到了<span lang=\"EN-US\">web</span>方面的<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>基础，学习了断点调试和<span lang=\"EN-US\">jutil</span>测试工具，<span lang=\"EN-US\">eclipse</span>快捷键，如<span lang=\"EN-US\">Ctrl+1</span>快速修复，<span lang=\"EN-US\">ctrl+</span>鼠标点击查看源码，<span lang=\"EN-US\">ctrl+shift+t</span>搜索源码，<span lang=\"EN-US\">ctrl+t</span>显示继承关系，<span lang=\"EN-US\">ctrl+alt+</span>上下：复制上一行，<span lang=\"EN-US\">alt+</span>上下：上下行换位置 。 了解了反射机制中反射类，方法，和字段的具体方法，反射用于编写框架。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">在算法学习上，解决了带分数，求黄金分割点<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>位小数，幸运数，错误票据，振兴中华和马虎的算式<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>道题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">带分数问题，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8964803\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8964803</span></a></span>。用<span lang=\"EN-US\">1-9</span>这<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>个数组成带分数的可能性，如：<span lang=\"EN-US\">100 </span>可以表示为带分数的形式：<span lang=\"EN-US\">100 = 3 + 69258 / 714</span>。此题 设<span lang=\"EN-US\">n = i+j/k; n</span>由用户给出，<span lang=\"EN-US\">j=(n-i)*k.</span>这样只需穷举另外两个变量，又因为<span lang=\"EN-US\">j&gt;k, &nbsp;</span>可知<span lang=\"EN-US\">k</span>最大为<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>位数， 加上限制条件后穷举并判断，还要去掉有<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>的情况。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">求黄金分割点小数点后<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>位<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8934767\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8934767</span></a></span>，由于黄金分割点是根<span lang=\"EN-US\">5-1</span>除<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>， 则求出根<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>的值再利用<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>类<span lang=\"EN-US\">BigDecimal</span>进行大数减和大数除即可。由于<span lang=\"EN-US\">Math.sqrt</span>方法最大位数达不到<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>位，则自行用数学方法求出根<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>。查找资料，最后使用牛顿迭代求根法。设函数<span lang=\"EN-US\">x^2 -5 = 0</span>，求方程的根。利用牛顿公式，<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Xn+1 = Xn - f(Xn)/f\'(Xn) &nbsp;</span>，再根据<span lang=\"EN-US\">X</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Xn+1</span>的差值确定精度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">幸运数，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8954609\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8954609</span></a></span>。找出规律得出所有幸运数再进行取部分即可。在判断过程，在每次去除要求的数集时，先将去掉的数改为<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>，最后再整体去<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>，免得单个去除之后，一次循环数的位置变化。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">错误票据，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8953420\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8953420</span></a></span>。首先要把几段数字组合进一个<span lang=\"EN-US\">HashSet</span>之后再进行处理。判断重号和缺号时，逐个加入判断重号，依据是否已经含有。从最小值判断到最大值可找到缺号。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">马虎的算式，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8927693\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8927693</span></a></span>。求如<span lang=\"EN-US\">27&nbsp; * 594 = 297 * 54&nbsp;</span>式的总个数。<st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"a\" sourcevalue=\"10\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">10a</span></st1:chmetcnv><span lang=\"EN-US\">+b * <st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"100\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">100c</st1:chmetcnv>+10d+e<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">= <st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"a\" sourcevalue=\"100\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">100a</st1:chmetcnv>+10d+b * <st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"10\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">10c</st1:chmetcnv>+e; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">设<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>个未知数<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>层<span lang=\"EN-US\">for</span>循环，每层由<span lang=\"EN-US\">1-9.</span>算出可能的值后减去出现重复数的值<span lang=\"EN-US\">(HashSet)</span>和前后相同值<span lang=\"EN-US\">(if <st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"a\" sourcevalue=\"10\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">10a</st1:chmetcnv>+b == <st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"10\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">10c</st1:chmetcnv> + e)</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">振兴中华，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8931363\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#6A3906;text-decoration:\r\nnone;text-underline:none\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8931363</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">。</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">采用树的深度遍历，每一步都有两种可能的走法，向下和向右，根据这个条件，写递归，</span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#006699;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">if</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#362E2B;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;\r\npadding:0cm;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(row+</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-