ht:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#362E2B;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;\r\npadding:0cm;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">); &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 19pt; line-height: 150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">其它方面，我负责带创新团队的三个新人，培养他们的同时也在锻炼自己的领导能力和管理能力。我觉得基础和视野比较重要，在过去的几个星期里，除了让他们了解业界动向，我给他们的任务是完成基础篇的学习。本周要进行测试（去年我们的机考内容），目标是放假之前做完二级课题并继续向前学习进阶篇内容。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</p>','2013-05-27 12:58:21'),(31,28,'2013/06/03 大二下第14周 javaweb学习 c#大作业 数据结构学习','<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">上周学习任务算法完成</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">4</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">道，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">javaweb</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">学习更新了</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">4</span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">天。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;算法分加为正方形数，<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9008251\" style=\"color: rgb(106, 57, 6); text-decoration: none;\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9008251</a>。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这是一道数学问题，求正方形内最多能放多少个小正方形。根据矩阵的规律，最后结果一定为边长的平方和：n*（n+1）(2n+!)/6。回忆到高中时推导平方和公式的时候，假设法，先推出结论，再假设当N时成立，最后证明n+1时也成立。现在用着当年高考的方法，真怀念。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;火柴游戏，<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9006041\" style=\"color: rgb(106, 57, 6); text-decoration: none;\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9006041</a>。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;只需找到没摆火柴的地方，上下没有&lsquo;1&rsquo;，左右没有&lsquo;-&rsquo;即可。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Card Trick,<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9006041\" style=\"color: rgb(106, 57, 6); text-decoration: none;\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/9006041</a>。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;河南省ACM难住我的题，还是当时太紧张了，想用循环链表，然后java实现比较困难，不如每次取余，只是结果为0时，判断一下取最后一位就行。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;数量周期，<a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8988732\" style=\"color: rgb(106, 57, 6); text-decoration: none;\">http://blog.csdn.net/zhangpengyu321/article/details/8988732</a>。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这是一道和自然相关的问题，求昆虫每年数量的规律。问题本身不难，当一个定值变化时，昆虫变化规律变化，这个值应该是对于生态系统的一个相对值，当值为2.5时，数量恒定，当值为3.2，数量在两个数间循环。求&nbsp;值为3.62时规律，编程后输出结果，发现数量呈不规则锯齿状。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在javaweb的学习中，学习了xml，http协议，密码学和https连接器的安全问题，和web资源访问流程。这学期也有xml课，但效果不佳，去的少，只学理论也不知道应用在哪里。现在想想，学一门课之前还是应该自己先深入了解一下它的应用。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; xml是一种相关数据保存的方式，常用作配置文件。对于&nbsp;xml，java也有一套增删改查的编程方法。比较重要的是Schema约束和DTD约束，Schema约束是XML文件，约束比较具体，而DTD约束是一个DTD格式的文件，约束较简单，只对元素和属性进行约束。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tomcat的内部结构，和各个目录的作用。发布项目时，可以放入Tomcat的webapps中直接发布，如果项目和服务器不在一个盘中，可进行虚拟映像，tomcat提供5种方式，其中一种不需要重启服务器的方式为在配置文件夹中的主机文件夹中建立一个XML文件，文件名为虚拟映像的文件名，内容为</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;其它方面，管理的三个大一新生，上周已经把address类基于TXT的增删改查考过了，考的并不好，不过在接下来的两天经过我的讲解已经可以参考着写出来了，但是自己什么都不参考再打出来可能有点问题，不过这些只能靠他们自己自觉了，接下来的计划是放假前提前做好二级课题，给他们选了题目，他们对五子棋和俄罗斯方块这些游戏比较感兴趣。选定题目后就会开始做。因为要还要准备考试，放假之前这4周就暂时安排了这一个任务。时间多的话会做一些算法题。</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(54, 46, 43); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我的本周计划是做c#大作业，也就是旅行足迹的windows版本，因为旅行足迹的核心还是对旅行记录进行时间和空间上的整理分类，鉴于数据会很大，只存在手机上不合适，还是需要用手机进行即时添加功能，而桌面版负责存储和后期修改查看。另外javaweb和算法都是向前更新5个。</p>','2013-06-03 13:20:15'),(32,28,'2013/06/11 大二下第15周 快考四级了','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这周准备考试的东西还有四级，再加上端午假期，计划没有完成。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">算法解决了古代赌局，关于概率的问题，请教了概率老师，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>有点失望，她没有告诉我用概率怎么求，而是让我去穷举。我觉得数量级达到<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>万明明就是让人用概率算的，哎，自己的概率也不是太好，做蓝桥杯也做了一段时间了，真是之前用不到的知识全都用到了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">解决了计算机图形学中用算法画直线，听起来很吊什么<span lang=\"EN-US\">dda</span>方法、<span lang=\"EN-US\">schma</span>方法，其实简单点就是求两点之间的点然后画出来，<span lang=\"EN-US\">x</span>的增量是<span lang=\"EN-US\">xi+</span>△<span lang=\"EN-US\">x,y</span>的增量是<span lang=\"EN-US\">yi+</span>△<span lang=\"EN-US\">y=yi+</span>△<span lang=\"EN-US\">x&middot;m&nbsp;</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">m</span>是斜率由给定的两点坐标求出，△<span lang=\"EN-US\">x</span>和△<span lang=\"EN-US\">y</span>则可以用<span lang=\"EN-US\">for</span>来遍历即可。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">javaweb</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">方面，详细地学习了<span lang=\"EN-US\">servlet</span>和这学期<span lang=\"EN-US\">javaweb</span>机考内容。<span lang=\"EN-US\">javaweb</span>不像<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>有些小问题很难发现，<span lang=\"EN-US\">servlet</span>地址少了个<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;/&rdquo;</span>让我<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">找了一下午才发现问题。学习了<span lang=\"EN-US\">servlet</span>的生命周期从创建一个实例开始，调用<span lang=\"EN-US\">init</span>（）方法，然后创建请求和响应对象，调用<span lang=\"EN-US\">service</span>（）方法处<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">理请求获得信息<span lang=\"EN-US\">Destroy()</span>不会自动关闭，只有在服务器关闭或主动结束<span lang=\"EN-US\">servlet</span>方法时，它才会调用<span lang=\"EN-US\">Destroy()</span>关闭。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">还是感觉自己的效率不高，我所理解的牛人是在同样的时间里能解决很多事情，而不是像我一样，选择了一些，其它事情时间就不够就必须<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">要放弃，效率还是要改善一下。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">本星期计划准备一下<span lang=\"EN-US\">xml</span>机考的<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>文件，做<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>道算法然后<span lang=\"EN-US\">web</span>更新<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>天。该考四级了，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>哎<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>听天由命了<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-06-11 18:22:25'),(33,28,'2013/8/20 苏州高博第一周','<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">坚持不易，周计划有很久没写。好东西也会被遗忘，其实是我的阵地太多，玩了十年的<span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ,</span>装满回忆的空间。还有一个贴吧，一个技术博客，<span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span>粉的微博，再加上杂七杂八的<span lang=\"EN-US\">facebook,twitter,vk~~~~~~ </span>怪不得有人说<span lang=\"EN-US\">hack</span>精神已经不远去，各种乱七八糟的平台，从事互联网的人们，开始用户至上， 培训师甚至有一些冠冕堂皇的理由教育程序员去<span lang=\"EN-US\">Ctrl c </span>。一切的很怪，互联网很怪。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">我是一个很早就有平台观念的人，我希望用户可以把所有的回忆都存在一个地方，很单纯的，随心所欲的。怪胎就像我，拥有各种平台，每一样都挥之不去。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">好吧，回到主题，高博呆了一周，大部分时间在自习，如果说有收获， 那就是第一个从早上<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>点到晚上<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>点都不闭眼的暑假。培训师也挺一般，重点是他没太在意我们这群享受<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>周短期免费培训的孩子。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">对<span lang=\"EN-US\">Java</span>接口有了更深的理解。我一直觉得有更深的东西，类似所谓的编程思想，我觉得一定有人可以用很通俗的语法说清楚这些事情的真相。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</p>','2013-08-20 09:20:15'),(34,29,'2013/10/10 大三上9月','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时间过的太快是永远不变的口头语，不过现在 还好，生活没有被我弄的太乱。只是目标很明确，做的还不到位。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">最近发现创业中心的<span lang=\"EN-US\">IP</span>是公网，这一年问了好多老师，他们 都说是内网， 学院的老师太坑了。人阿，还是有主见点好，信谁都不 一定靠谱了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现在手里有几台服务器，虽然配置不算好，但肯定是够 了，大学这几年也学到很多，享有资源而无作为的人真心是一无是处的垃圾。不要报怨资源不好不够，现有的资源都用好<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现在目标很明确了，这是个社交的时代，没有服务器太落后了。现在，有了，能做到什么样就凭自己的本事了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height:17.65pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#362E2B\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-10-10 13:31:31'),(35,28,'2013/10/30 大三上第8周','<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">这一周一直在学习</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">，杨尚川的录的视频太不给力了，从他身上我看到了一个码农语言表达能力的未来</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">&hellip;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">看视频花了不少时间，还好挺顺，除了听的时候很痛苦，过程中没有遇到问题，感觉还是效率太低了，看视频看教程都是一步步的来，很少自己思考。这个问题比较严重，要改改了。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">说好的每天做一道算法题说了一年多了，说了一年多了。。。再加个劲。。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这周写了五篇博文，分别是<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span>概述、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span>配置和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Nutch</span>概述、配置和<span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span>整合。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分布式系统就是分布式软件系统，包括分布式操作系统、分布式数据库和分布式文件系统等，<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span>属于其中的文件系统，它实现了分布式文件系统和部分分布式数据库系统的功能。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span>分布式文件系统由一个名字结点和多个数据结点组成，文件在<span lang=\"EN-US\">HDFS</span>底层被分成了多个<span lang=\"EN-US\">Block,</span>这些<span lang=\"EN-US\">block</span>存在数据结点上，<span lang=\"EN-US\">block</span>一般被复制存储到其它数据结点上，达到数据的高容错性和安全性，而名字结点记录和控制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分布式推崇本地计算，因为传递计算比传递数据经济，数据在哪台机子上就由哪台机子计算 ，尽量少的进行网络传输。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Block</span>默认<st1:chmetcnv tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"False\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"64\" unitname=\"m\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">64M</span></st1:chmetcnv><span lang=\"EN-US\">, block</span>大小是要是为了最大限度的本地计算。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">Map</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">和<span lang=\"EN-US\">Reduce</span>没有仔细研究，大概就是对计算的中间结果不断的<span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">reduce</span>，最终<span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span>成最终结果。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配置分布式系统的过程是：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下载配置<span lang=\"EN-US\"> jdk hadoop ssh</span>。为了方便管理配置主机名，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">/etc/hostname</span>配置自己的主机名，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">hosts</span>下配置其它主机的主机名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配制免密钥的<span lang=\"EN-US\">SSH,</span>保证主机能够直接通信，通过<span lang=\"EN-US\">ssh keygen</span>生成公钥，将<span lang=\"EN-US\">Master</span>生成的公钥存于其它<span lang=\"EN-US\">slaver</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">authorized_keys</span>中。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop,<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">a</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）在<span lang=\"EN-US\">/hadoop/conf/hadoop-env.sh</span>中添加<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>的环境变量<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">b) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hdfs-site.xml</span>中配置主机数，<span lang=\"EN-US\">dfs.replication, </span>若集群主机数少于这个数字<span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop</span>会出问题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">c) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">core-site.xml</span>中配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">namenode</span>的地址和端口号<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">d) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在<span lang=\"EN-US\">mapred-site.xml</span>中配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">jobtracker</span>的地址和端口号<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">e) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">master</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">slaver<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">然后要格式化一次<span lang=\"EN-US\">namenode</span>，多次格式化会出问题，要手工修改<span lang=\"EN-US\">namespaceID,</span>启动<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hadoop</span>需要关闭防火墙，<span lang=\"EN-US\">IPS</span>工具可检测各个节点是否开启成功，有问题看<span lang=\"EN-US\">hadoop/logs </span>日至、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">Nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的大概过程是无限重复：注入链接<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span>生成<span lang=\"EN-US\">crawldb-</span>抓取<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span>解析<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span>反转链接生成<span lang=\"EN-US\">linkdb(</span>为了检索<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">Nutch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会保存网页元数据和文本数据。所有链接。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">具体对网页的检索需要<span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span>，他是<span lang=\"EN-US\">lucene</span>的衍生，然后<span lang=\"EN-US\">solr</span>对中文的分词不太好，还要配置<span lang=\"EN-US\">mmseg4j</span>分词。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>','2013-10-30 21:07:56'),(36,24,'Nutch入门教程四 url过滤策略','<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">Nutch</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">的使用中如果需要对</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">Url</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">抓取策略进行定制修改，应该在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">conf/regex-urlfilter.txt</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">中进行配置，文件里讲的很清楚了</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">默认配置跳过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">file</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ftp</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">mailto</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这些地址：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#skip file: file: ftp: and mailto: urls</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">-^(file|ftp|mailto):</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">跳过了所有的图片和不能爬取的后缀：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#skip image and other suffixes we can&rsquo;t yet parse</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">-\\.(gif|GIF|jpg</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&hellip;&hellip;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">)$</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">跳过了所有动态网页，也就是带有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?*!@=</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这些符号的网页</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#skip URLs containing certain charater as probable queries, etc.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">-[?*!@=]</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">因为要抓的是淘宝，这里要把它引掉，不进行过滤。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">然后就是抓取其它所有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#accept anything else</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">+.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这是用到了正则表达式的知识，在我看来，对于一个小码农来说，开发就是不断的深度优先遍历，总是不断的发现不会的东西然后去学习。中</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">+-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">就是添加和排除规则</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:18.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\ncolor:#2A2A2A\">\\</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#2A2A2A\">是转义符</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n9.0pt;line-height:150%;color:#2A2A2A\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">^</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示匹配字符串开始的位置</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示匹配除</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之外的任何单个字符</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">$</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示匹配字符串结局的位置</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示可匹配前面前后字符</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">zo*</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">可匹配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">z</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">zoo</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示匹配后面的字条</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">zo</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">只能匹配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">zoo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> zooo </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">不能匹配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">z</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">表示零次或一次匹配前面的字符或子表达式。例如，&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">do(es)?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;匹配&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">do</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;或&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">does</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;中的</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">do</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">{n}</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">n&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是非负整数。正好匹配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;n&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">次。例如，&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o{2}</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;与&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bob</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;中的&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;不匹配，但与&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">food</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中的两个&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;匹配。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">{n,}</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">n&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是非负整数。至少匹配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;n&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">次。例如，&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o{2,}</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;不匹配&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Bob</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;中的&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;，而匹配&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">foooood</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中的所有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> o</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o{1,}</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&rdquo;等效于&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">o+</