mes=\"\" style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">更合适的了，只能用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">把开始时间和结束时间建立联系，然后用结束时间查找开始时间进行判断。</span></p>','2013-11-03 17:12:35'),(39,32,'记忆化搜索-01背包问题','<p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">N</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">个重量和价值分别为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">w</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">v</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的物品。从中选出总重量不超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">W</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的物品，求价值最大方案。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">样例：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">n=4</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2,3&nbsp; 1,2&nbsp; 3,4&nbsp; 2,2 </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">W=5</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">最基本的想法，求出重价比，从高向低试。然后我发现了一些数据结构上的一些问题，我没有办法用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">把</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> weight</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">value</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> w-v </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">关联。</span> <span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">我想到了用两个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">map</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">分别把三个值关联，但是这样的处理有些问题，因为这些值并不是是唯一的，这样一来，就麻烦了。因为如果我想把它们排序之后依然对应，就得有唯一确定的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ID, </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">如果重写一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Collections</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">sort</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">方法，那就太怪异了一点。所以只能根据初始写入时给一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">id</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。暂时想不到更好的办法。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">但是我发现我成功的躲避了作者通过