ng=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\r\n\" courier=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">问题出现了，为什么</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">array</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">放在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">里和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">外差别这么大呢。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">首先列出所有情况：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">根据输入大小在循环中动态定义</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">array</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">大小，最后消耗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2836kb</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中定义</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">array[1001][1001] </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">消耗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4378kb</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在循环中定义</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">array[1001][1001] </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">消耗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11809kb</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">外定义</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static array[1001][1001] </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">消耗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">691kb</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">针对这些不同，我尝试在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">方法中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">new</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">出一个非静态方法，也就是做到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">array[1001][1001]</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">仍然在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">main</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">方法之外，但不是静态的。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">结果消耗内存和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">相似。这就可以说明内存的差距出自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的数组。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">静态数组是在声明时已经确定子数组大小的数组，即数组元素的个数固定不变。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中的数组是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">new</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">出来的，所以存放在堆内存中，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">出的数组当然是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">区中。大家都知道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的堆是很费内存的，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">static</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，也就是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的类变量，不管有多少个实例，都会共用一个内存空间，</span> <span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">所以内存耗费最少。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;mso-line-height-alt:16.5pt\">详细的<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>内存分配详解：<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\';\"><a href=\"http://www.98ki.com/blog/servlet/HomeServlet?method=get&amp;id=43\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#555555;text-decoration:none;text-underline:\r\nnone\">Java</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" trebuchet=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">内存区域分析</span></span></a><o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-11-08 15:19:54'),(47,35,'Hibernate+Maven+MyEclipse基础配置','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">Java</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">是面向对象的语言，对象模型，其主要概念是继承、关联、多态等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">;</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">数据库是关系模型，其主要概念是：表、主键、外键等。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">解决这个模型不匹配有两种方法：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.jdbc</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">手工转换</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2.ORM(Object Relation Mapping)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">对象关系映射框架来解决。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">:hibernate,OJB </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">等。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这里使用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Maven</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">作为项目管理工具。首先创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Maven</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">项目</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，手工添加三个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">source flolder</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如下。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><img src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/35.jpg\" alt=\"http://www.98ki.com//blogImg/35.jpg\" class=\"decoded\" style=\"line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">然后在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">MyEclipse</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">的数据库操作台添加数据库连接驱动，这里默认</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">MySql</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">，如下图，成功之后会自动生成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">Hibernate.cfg.xml</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">HibernateSessionFactory</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 宋体;\">。</span><img width=\"561\" height=\"643\" src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/34.jpg\" alt=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/34.jpg\" class=\"decoded shrinkToFit\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list 18.0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">1. Hibernate</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">安装配置</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">pom.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中加入</span></p>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><dependency><o:p></o:p></dependency></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <groupid>org.hibernate</groupid><o:p></o:p></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<artifactid>hibernate-core</artifactid><o:p></o:p></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <version><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"30\" month=\"12\" year=\"1899\" w:st=\"on\">4.2.6</st1:chsdate>.Final</version><o:p></o:p></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></pre>\r\n<pre style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></pre>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">a. hibernate.cfg.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中主要配置数据库</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">URL,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">用户名，密码，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">JDBC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">驱动等。启动时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hibernate</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">classpath</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中找到这个配置。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">加载</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hibernate.cfg.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的类是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HibernateSessionFactory</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">映射文件（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hbm.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">annoutation</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">方式，对象模型和关系模型的映射）。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">顾名思义，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">hbm.xml</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">就是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">xml</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中配置映射，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">annoutation</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">就是在实体类中以注解的方式配置映射。两种方式皆可。这里使用注解方式。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在数据库操作台上选择要生成的表右键</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">-&gt; hibernate reverses engineering,</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">操作如下图。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img width=\"580\" height=\"643\" src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/36.jpg\" alt=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/36.jpg\" class=\"shrinkToFit decoded\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img width=\"580\" height=\"643\" src=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/37.jpg\" alt=\"http://www.98ki.com/blogImg/37.jpg\" class=\"shrinkToFit decoded\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span new=\"\" times=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\">成功之后会在选择的包中生成的带注解的实体类。如下图：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-13 13:18:55'),(48,37,'正则表达式用法查询表','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;正则表达式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[1]</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的&ldquo;鼻祖&rdquo;或许可一直追溯到科学家对人类神经系统工作原理的早期研究。美国新泽西州的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Warren McCulloch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和出生在美国底特律的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Walter Pitts</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">这两位神经生理方面的科学家，研究出了一种用数学方式来描述神经网络的新方法，他们创造性地将神经系统中的神经元描述成了小而简单的自动控制元，从而作出了一项伟大的工作革新。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1956 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">出生在被马克&middot;吐温（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mark Twain</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">）称为&ldquo;美国最美丽的城市之一&rdquo;的哈特福德市的一位名叫</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stephen Kleene</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的数学科学家，他在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Warren McCulloch</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Walter Pitts</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">早期工作的基础之上，发表了一篇题目是《神经网事件的表示法》的论文，利用称之为正则集合的数学符号来描述此模型，引入了正则表达式的概念。正则表达式被作为用来描述其称之为&ldquo;正则集的代数&rdquo;的一种表达式，因而采用了&ldquo;正则表达式&rdquo;这个术语。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之后一段时间，人们发现可以将这一工作成果应用于其他方面。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ken Thompson</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">就把这一成果应用于计算搜索算法的一些早期研究，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Ken Thompson</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> Unix</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的主要发明人，也就是大名鼎鼎的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Unix</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之父。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Unix</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">之父将此符号系统引入编辑器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QED</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，然后是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Unix</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">上的编辑器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ed</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，并最终引入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">grep</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jeffrey Friedl </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">在其著作《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Mastering Regular Expressions (2nd edition)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">》（中文版译作：精通正则表达式，已出到第三版）中对此作了进一步阐述讲解，如果你希望更多了解正则表达式理论和历史，推荐你看看这本书。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">自此以后，正则表达式被广泛地应用到各种</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">UNIX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">或类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">UNIX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的工具中，如大家熟知的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Perl</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Perl</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">的正则表达式源自于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Henry Spencer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">编写的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">regex</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，之后已演化成了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">pcre</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Perl</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">兼容正则表达式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Perl Compatible Regular Expressions</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">），</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">pcre</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是一个由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Philip Hazel</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">开发的、为很多现代工具所使用的库。正则表达式的第一个实用应用程序即为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Unix</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">中的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> qed </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">编辑器。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">然后，正则表达式在各种计算机语言或各种应用领域得到了广大的应用和发展，演变成为计算机技术森林中的一只形神美丽且声音动听的百灵鸟。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<table log-set-param=\"table_view\" class=\"table-view log-set-param\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 5px 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">元字符</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">描述</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">将下一个字符标记为一个特殊字符、或一个原义字符、或一个向后引用、或一个八进制转义符。例如，&ldquo;\\n&rdquo;匹配一个换行符。&ldquo;\\\\n&rdquo;匹配字符&quot;n&quot;。序列&ldquo;\\\\&rdquo;匹配&ldquo;\\&rdquo;而&ldquo;\\(&rdquo;则匹配&ldquo;(&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">^</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配输入字符串的开始位置。如果设置了RegExp对象的Multiline属性，^也匹配&ldquo;\\n&rdquo;或&ldquo;\\r&rdquo;之后的位置。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">$</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配输入字符串的结束位置。如果设置了RegExp对象的Multiline属性，$也匹配&ldquo;\\n&rdquo;或&ldquo;\\r&rdquo;之前的位置。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">*</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配前面的子表达式零次或多次。例如，zo*能匹配&ldquo;z&rdquo;以及&ldquo;zoo&rdquo;。*等价于{0,}。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">+</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配前面的子表达式一次或多次。例如，&ldquo;zo+&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;zo&rdquo;以及&ldquo;zoo&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;z&rdquo;。+等价于{1,}。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">?</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配前面的子表达式零次或一次。例如，&ldquo;do(es)?&rdquo;可以匹配&ldquo;does&rdquo;或&ldquo;does&rdquo;中的&ldquo;do&rdquo;。?等价于{0,1}。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">{n}</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">n是一个非负整数。匹配确定的n次。例如，&ldquo;o{2}&rdquo;不能匹配&ldquo;Bob&rdquo;中的&ldquo;o&rdquo;，但是能匹配&ldquo;food&rdquo;中的两个o。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">{n,}</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">n是一个非负整数。至少匹配n次。例如，&ldquo;o{2,}&rdquo;不能匹配&ldquo;Bob&rdquo;中的&ldquo;o&rdquo;，但能匹配&ldquo;foooood&rdquo;中的所有o。&ldquo;o{1,}&rdquo;等价于&ldquo;o+&rdquo;。&ldquo;o{0,}&rdquo;则等价于&ldquo;o*&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">{n,m}</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">m和n均为非负整数，其中n&lt;=m。最少匹配n次且最多匹配m次。例如，&ldquo;o{1,3}&rdquo;将匹配&ldquo;fooooood&rdquo;中的前三个o。&ldquo;o{0,1}&rdquo;等价于&ldquo;o?&rdquo;。请注意在逗号和两个数之间不能有空格。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">?</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">当该字符紧跟在任何一个其他限制符（*,+,?，{n}，{n,}，{n,m}）后面时，匹配模式是非贪婪的。非贪婪模式尽可能少的匹配所搜索的字符串，而默认的贪婪模式则尽可能多的匹配所搜索的字符串。例如，对于字符串&ldquo;oooo&rdquo;，&ldquo;o?&rdquo;将匹配单个&ldquo;o&rdquo;，而&ldquo;o+&rdquo;将匹配所有&ldquo;o&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">.点</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配除&ldquo;\\n&rdquo;之外的任何单个字符。要匹配包括&ldquo;\\n&rdquo;在内的任何字符，请使用像&ldquo;[\\s\\S]&rdquo;的模式。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(pattern)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配pattern并获取这一匹配。所获取的匹配可以从产生的Matches集合得到，在VBScript中使用SubMatches集合，在JScript中则使用$0&hellip;$9属性。要匹配圆括号字符，请使用&ldquo;\\(&rdquo;或&ldquo;\\)&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(?:pattern)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配pattern但不获取匹配结果，也就是说这是一个非获取匹配，不进行存储供以后使用。这在使用或字符&ldquo;(|)&rdquo;来组合一个模式的各个部分是很有用。例如&ldquo;industr(?:y|ies)&rdquo;就是一个比&ldquo;industry|industries&rdquo;更简略的表达式。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(?=pattern)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">正向肯定预查，在任何匹配pattern的字符串开始处匹配查找字符串。这是一个非获取匹配，也就是说，该匹配不需要获取供以后使用。例如，&ldquo;Windows(?=95|98|NT|2000)&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;Windows2000&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;Windows3.1&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;。预查不消耗字符，也就是说，在一个匹配发生后，在最后一次匹配之后立即开始下一次匹配的搜索，而不是从包含预查的字符之后开始。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(?!pattern)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">正向否定预查，在任何不匹配pattern的字符串开始处匹配查找字符串。这是一个非获取匹配，也就是说，该匹配不需要获取供以后使用。例如&ldquo;Windows(?!95|98|NT|2000)&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;Windows3.1&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;Windows2000&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(?&lt;=pattern)</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">反向肯定预查，与正向肯定预查类似，只是方向相反。例如，&ldquo;(?&lt;=95|98|NT|2000)Windows&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;2000Windows&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;3.1Windows&rdquo;中的&ldquo;Windows&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">(?<!--pattern)</div--></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">反向否定预查，与正向否定预查类似，只是方向相反。例如&ldquo;(?<!--95|98|NT|2000)Windows”能匹配“3.1Windows”中的“Windows”，但不能匹配“2000Windows”中的“Windows”。</div--></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">x|y</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配x或y。例如，&ldquo;z|food&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;z&rdquo;或&ldquo;food&rdquo;。&ldquo;(z|f)ood&rdquo;则匹配&ldquo;zood&rdquo;或&ldquo;food&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">[xyz]</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">字符集合。匹配所包含的任意一个字符。例如，&ldquo;[abc]&rdquo;可以匹配&ldquo;plain&rdquo;中的&ldquo;a&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">[^xyz]</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">负值字符集合。匹配未包含的任意字符。例如，&ldquo;[^abc]&rdquo;可以匹配&ldquo;plain&rdquo;中的&ldquo;plin&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">[a-z]</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">字符范围。匹配指定范围内的任意字符。例如，&ldquo;[a-z]&rdquo;可以匹配&ldquo;a&rdquo;到&ldquo;z&rdquo;范围内的任意小写字母字符。</div>\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">注意:只有连字符在字符组内部时,并且出两个字符之间时,才能表示字符的范围; 如果出字符组的开头,则只能表示连字符本身.</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">[^a-z]</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">负值字符范围。匹配任何不在指定范围内的任意字符。例如，&ldquo;[^a-z]&rdquo;可以匹配任何不在&ldquo;a&rdquo;到&ldquo;z&rdquo;范围内的任意字符。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\b</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个单词边界，也就是指单词和空格间的位置。例如，&ldquo;er\\b&rdquo;可以匹配&ldquo;never&rdquo;中的&ldquo;er&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;verb&rdquo;中的&ldquo;er&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\B</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配非单词边界。&ldquo;er\\B&rdquo;能匹配&ldquo;verb&rdquo;中的&ldquo;er&rdquo;，但不能匹配&ldquo;never&rdquo;中的&ldquo;er&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\cx</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配由x指明的控制字符。例如，\\cM匹配一个Control-M或回车符。x的值必须为A-Z或a-z之一。否则，将c视为一个原义的&ldquo;c&rdquo;字符。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"75\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\d</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\"658\" align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个数字字符。等价于[0-9]。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\D</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个非数字字符。等价于[^0-9]。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\f</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个换页符。等价于\\x0c和\\cL。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\n</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个换行符。等价于\\x0a和\\cJ。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\r</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个回车符。等价于\\x0d和\\cM。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\s</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配任何空白字符，包括空格、制表符、换页符等等。等价于[ \\f\\n\\r\\t\\v]。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\S</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配任何非空白字符。等价于[^ \\f\\n\\r\\t\\v]。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\t</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个制表符。等价于\\x09和\\cI。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\v</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配一个垂直制表符。等价于\\x0b和\\cK。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\w</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配包括下划线的任何单词字符。等价于&ldquo;[A-Za-z0-9_]&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\W</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配任何非单词字符。等价于&ldquo;[^A-Za-z0-9_]&rdquo;。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\xn</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配n，其中n为十六进制转义值。十六进制转义值必须为确定的两个数字长。例如，&ldquo;\\x41&rdquo;匹配&ldquo;A&rdquo;。&ldquo;\\x041&rdquo;则等价于&ldquo;\\x04&amp;1&rdquo;。正则表达式中可以使用ASCII编码。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\num</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配num，其中num是一个正整数。对所获取的匹配的引用。例如，&ldquo;(.)\\1&rdquo;匹配两个连续的相同字符。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\n</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">标识一个八进制转义值或一个向后引用。如果\\n之前至少n个获取的子表达式，则n为向后引用。否则，如果n为八进制数字（0-7），则n为一个八进制转义值。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\nm</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">标识一个八进制转义值或一个向后引用。如果\\nm之前至少有nm个获得子表达式，则nm为向后引用。如果\\nm之前至少有n个获取，则n为一个后跟文字m的向后引用。如果前面的条件都不满足，若n和m均为八进制数字（0-7），则\\nm将匹配八进制转义值nm。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\nml</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">如果n为八进制数字（0-7），且m和l均为八进制数字（0-7），则匹配八进制转义值nml。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">\\un</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\r\n            <div class=\"para\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 25px;\">匹配n，其中n是一个用四个十六进制数字表示的Unicode字符。例如，\\u00A9匹配版权符号（&copy;）。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\\&lt; \\&gt;</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">匹配词（word）的开始（\\&lt;）和结束（\\&gt;）。例如正则表达式\\</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">\\( \\)</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">将 \\( 和 \\) 之间的表达式定义为&ldquo;组&rdquo;（group），并且将匹配这个表达式的字符保存到一个临时区域（一个正则表达式中最多可以保存9个），它们可以用 \\1 到\\9 的符号来引用。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">|</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">将两个匹配条件进行逻辑&ldquo;或&rdquo;（Or）运算。例如正则表达式(him|her) 匹配&quot;it belongs to him&quot;和&quot;it belongs to her&quot;，但是不能匹配&quot;it belongs to them.&quot;。注意：这个元字符不是所有的软件都支持的。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">+</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">匹配1或多个正好在它之前的那个字符。例如正则表达式9+匹配9、99、999等。注意：这个元字符不是所有的软件都支持的。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">?</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">匹配0或1个正好在它之前的那个字符。注意：这个元字符不是所有的软件都支持的。</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">{i} {i,j}</td>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" valign=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 10px; height: 22px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\">匹配指定数目的字符，这些字符是在它之前的表达式定义的。例如正则表达式A[0-9]{3} 能够匹配字符&quot;A&quot;后面跟着正好3个数字字符的串，例如A123、A348等，但是不匹配A1234。而正则表达式[0-9]{4,6} 匹配连续的任意4个、5个或者6个数字</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-13 17:10:39'),(49,49,'在截取的HTML文档中匹配补全标签','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在博客的首页博文展示中做了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HTML</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">截取，每个博文展示</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">个字符，包括语法标签在内，然后发现博客内容标签和页面</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">HTML</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">标签会混乱，一般情况还好，如果还个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">table</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">什么的，整个首页全乱了。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">之前打算在后台匹配补全标签，大致思想是检索标签，然后对标签进行入栈出栈操作。。但是想想，如果有一个控制子文档不影响的父文档的标签就不用这么费资源了。如果前台能完成还是不要用网线到处传</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">String</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">了。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">最后还是找到了一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">js</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的过滤函数。这个方法还是能够解决大部分问题的，一些比较狠的，比如去表格，本身也就没办法去很好的部分表现，尽量避免不正常情况吧。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">js</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">果然简单强大，看了这个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">for</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">我还是决定改写一下这个匹配算法。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#D9D9D9\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><script type=\"text/javascript\"> <br />\r\nfunction closeHTML(str){ <br />\r\nvar arrTags=[\"span\",\"font\",\"b\",\"u\",\"i\",\"h1\",\"h2\",\"h3\",\"h4\",\"h5\",\"h6\",\"p\",\"li\",\"ul\",\"table\",\"div\"]; <br />\r\nfor(var i=0;i<arrTags.length;i++){ <br />\r\nvar intOpen=0; <br />\r\nvar intClose=0; <br />\r\nvar re=new RegExp(\"\\\\<\"+arrTags[i]+\"( [^\\\\<\\\\>]+|)\\\\>\",\"ig\"); <br />\r\nvar arrMatch=str.match(re); <br />\r\nif(arrMatch!=null) intOpen=arrMatch.length; <br />\r\nre=new RegExp(\"\\\\<\\\\/\"+arrTags[i]+\"\\\\>\",\"ig\"); <br />\r\narrMatch=str.match(re); <br />\r\nif(arrMatch!=null) intClose=arrMatch.length; <br />\r\nfor(var j=0;j<intOpen-intClose;j++){ <br />\r\nstr+=\"</\"+arrTags[i]+\">\"; <br />\r\n} <br />\r\n/*for(var j=(intOpen-intClose-1);j>=0;j--){ <br />\r\nstr+=\"</\"+arrTags[i]+\">\"; <br />\r\n}*/ <br />\r\n} <br />\r\nreturn str; <br />\r\n} <br />\r\n</script>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-13 17:59:44'),(50,28,'2013/11/13 大三上第11周','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">在爬虫方面，在来往上问了几个大神，少符大神说：&ldquo;抓页面的同时抓异步请求&rdquo;，这句话听起来简单，然后我算是没听懂。云镭大神帮我转邮件问了&ldquo;专业人士&rdquo;，让我用<span lang=\"EN-US\">webkit</span>渲染，说是有相关开源的东西，传地址然后就回数据，<span lang=\"EN-US\">webkit</span>我是看了，架构比较复杂，顶层也不是<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>封装，<span lang=\"EN-US\">js</span>对<span lang=\"EN-US\">webkit</span>的开源找到一个，有点问题，还没找到合适的。抚狄大神说<span lang=\"EN-US\">ajax</span>很麻烦，要做浏览器渲染，爬外边的<span lang=\"EN-US\">B<st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"2\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\">2C</st1:chmetcnv></span>比较靠谱，不建议爬<span lang=\"EN-US\">AJAX</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">然后还是没什么突破性的进展，就是发现了更多问题，比如商品价格在源码里，但实际价格是折扣后价格，在大概一秒左右之后才会动态加载，如果速度快，在浏览器里可以看到这个变化。然后就是同一个商品不同价格问题，<st1:chmetcnv unitname=\"C\" sourcevalue=\"3\" hasspace=\"False\" negative=\"False\" numbertype=\"1\" tcsc=\"0\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3c</span></st1:chmetcnv>里最多，什么套餐一套餐二，带线不带线的，想想就晕了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">这星期还是在研究动态规划方面的算法，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.98ki.com/blog/servlet/HomeServlet?method=get&amp;id=46\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">动态规划</span></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">-</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;text-decoration:none;\r\ntext-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">最长子串问题</span></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">LCS</span></a></span>。除了算法本身，还学习了<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>内存区相关问题。把<span lang=\"EN-US\">List</span>定义成静态之后 ，内存使用比非静态少了<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>倍。因为<span lang=\"EN-US\">List</span>是创建出的对象，在<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>中<span lang=\"EN-US\"> new</span>出的对象和数组都在堆内存中，<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>的堆内存每次都会创建不同的内存空间，而静态代码区不管实例化多少对象都共用一个内存空间。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">在网上收集了一些，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.98ki.com/blog/servlet/HomeServlet?method=get&amp;id=43\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:\r\nnone\">Java</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">内存区域分析</span></span></a></span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>中除了堆栈寄存器，还有一块方法区，存放普通方法、静态方法、常量和字符串。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">Java Web</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体\">的课程三大框架中<span lang=\"EN-US\"> Struts2</span>已经学完了，现在在学习<span lang=\"EN-US\">Hibernate, <a href=\"http://www.98ki.com/blog/servlet/HomeServlet?method=get&amp;id=47\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:\r\nnone\">Hibernate + Maven+ MyEclipse</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">基础配置</span></span></a></span>。发现<span lang=\"EN-US\">Maven</span>真心方便，现在的<span lang=\"EN-US\">MyEclipse</span>也真心强大，直接生成所有配置文件和带<span lang=\"EN-US\">Annoutation</span>方式映射的实体类。顿时就觉得机考的时候完蛋了，机房肯定什么都没有。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">然后网站也在一步步地建设，在博文的展示中，用<span lang=\"EN-US\">JS</span>解决了首页截取博文展示之后的<span lang=\"EN-US\">HTML</span>标签不匹配问题： <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.98ki.com/blog/servlet/HomeServlet?method=get&amp;id=49\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">在截取的</span></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:windowtext;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\">HTML</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:windowtext;\r\ntext-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">文档中匹配补全标签</span></span></a></span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;font-weight:normal\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>','2013-11-13 21:29:01'),(51,35,'三大框架之整合spring','<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">三大框架整合</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">spring</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">，首先通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Maven</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: