ont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">防止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">spring</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">内存溢出监听器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> --&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;listener&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;listener-class&gt;org.springframework.web.util.IntrospectorCleanupListener&lt;/listener-class&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/listener&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&lt;/web-app&gt;</span></p>','2013-11-20 16:49:35'),(53,52,' java Runtime Data Areas（官方版java 虚拟机运行环境数据区域说明）','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;The Java virtual machine defines various runtime data areas that are used during execution of a program. Some of these data areas are created on&nbsp;Java virtual machine start-up and are destroyed only when the Java virtual machine exits. Other data areas are per thread.&nbsp;Per-thread data areas are created when a thread is created and destroyed when the thread exits.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">每个线程都拥有自己的数据区，在线程启动的时候创建，在线程消亡的时候销毁。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1. PC Register</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Java virtual machine can support many threads of execution at once.Each Java virtual machine thread has its own&nbsp;PC (program counter) register. At any point, each Java virtual machine thread is executing the code of a single method, the current method&nbsp;for that thread. If that method is not NATIVE, the PC register contains the address of the Java virtual machine instruction currently being executed. If the method currently being executed by the thread is NATIVE, the value of the Java virtual machine\'s PC register is undefined. The Java virtual machine\'s PC&nbsp;register is wide enough to hold a returnAddress or a native pointer on the specific platform.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">支持同时有许多线程在运行，每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">线程都拥有自己的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC Register</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。在每个时刻，每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">线程在执行一个该线程当前的方法。若该方法不是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NATIVE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">代码，则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC Register</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">包括了当前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">执行的指令。若该方法是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NATIVE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">代码，则不会定义</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC Register</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PC Register</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的数据范围足够容纳返回地址和所依赖的平台上本地指针。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.&nbsp;Stacks</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Each Java virtual machine thread has a private Java virtual machine stack, created at the same time as the thread.&nbsp;A Java virtual machine stack stores frames. A Java virtual machine stack is analogous to the stack of a conventional language such as C: it holds local variables and partial results, and plays a part in method invocation and return. Because the Java virtual machine stack is never manipulated directly except to push and pop frames, frames may be heap allocated. The memory for a Java virtual machine stack does not need to be contiguous.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">线程都有一个私有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stack,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在线程创建的时候随之产生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">存储的是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">frames. jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">类似于传统的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">C</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">语的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">：存储局部变量和返回结果，与方法的调用和返回有关。因为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">从来不是被直接操作除了压入、弹出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">frame</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">之外，所以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">frames</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以是堆分配的。每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的内存也没有必要是连续的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; The Java virtual machine specification permits Java virtual machine stacks either to be of a fixed size or to dynamically expand and contract as required by the computation. If the Java virtual machine stacks are of a fixed size, the size of each Java virtual machine stack may be chosen independently when that stack is created. A Java virtual machine implementation may provide the programmer or the user control over the initial size of Java virtual machine stacks, as well as, in the case of dynamically expanding or contracting Java virtual machine stacks, control over the maximum and minimum sizes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;jvm Specification</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">允许</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">为固定大小，也充许根据估计值动态的扩展。如果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">是固定大小，则创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的时候，每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">大小都是独立选择的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的实现可能支持编程人员和用户控制在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的初始大小的基础上控制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的大小，同样地在动态地扩展或缩小</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的大小这种情况下，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">大小在最大最小值之间。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以产生两种异常：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">若一个线程估算的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">超出了允许的范围，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">StackOverflowError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以动态扩展，当线程企图扩展但是没有足够的内存实现这种扩展，或者没有足够的内存为新的线程分配初始</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">空间时，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OutOfMemoryError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. Heap</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;The Java virtual machine has a&nbsp;heap&nbsp;that is shared among all Java virtual machine threads. The heap is the runtime data area from which memory for all class instances and arrays is allocated.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">heap</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">是被所有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">线程共享的一块区域。所有的类实例和数组都是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中分配内存。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; The heap is created on virtual machine start-up. Heap storage for objects is reclaimed by an automatic storage management system (known as a garbage collector); objects are never explicitly deallocated. The Java virtual machine assumes no particular type of automatic storage management system, and the storage management technique may be chosen according to the implementor\'s system requirements. The heap may be of a fixed size or may be expanded as required by the computation and may be contracted if a larger heap becomes unnecessary. The memory for the heap does not need to be contiguous.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">启动的时候创建的，它存储对象</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Objects</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，这些</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">objects</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以被</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">回收，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">objects</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">从来不会被显示的销毁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">没有特定的存储自动管理系统，存储管理技术可以根据需要实现的系统要求进行选择。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以是固定的大小，也可以是根据估算进行扩展，也可以缩小如果一个比较大的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">变得无用时。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的内存不要求是连续的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Java virtual machine implementation may provide the programmer or the user control over the initial size of the heap, as well as, if the heap can be dynamically expanded or contracted, control over the maximum and minimum heap size.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的实现可能提供编程人员和用户在初始大小的基础上控制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的大小，如果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以动态的扩展或者缩小，则可以在最大小最值的基础上灵活控制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Z</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; jvm Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以产生一种异常：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如果估算出的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">大小超出了存储系统管理的存储范围，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">将抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OutOfMemoryError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4. Method Area</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The Java virtual machine has a method area that is shared among all Java virtual machine threads. The method area is analogous to the storage area for compiled code of a conventional language or analogous to the &quot;text&quot; segment in a UNIX process. It stores per-class structures such as the runtime constant pool, field and method data, and the code for methods and constructors, including the special methods used in class and instance initialization and interface type initialization.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; Method Area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">由所有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">线程共享。它存储每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的结构，比如说运行时常量池、域、方法数据、方法体、构造函数、包括类中的专用方法、实例初始化、接口初始化。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The method area is created on virtual machine start-up. Although the method area is logically part of the heap, simple implementations may choose not to either garbage collect or compact it. This version of the Java virtual machine specification does not mandate the location of the method area or the policies used to manage compiled code. The method area may be of a fixed size or may be expanded as required by the computation and may be contracted if a larger method area becomes unnecessary. The memory for the method area does not need to be contiguous.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Method Area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">启动的时候创建。尽管</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在逻辑上是属于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Heap</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的一部分，但是实现上一般可以选择不被回收或者紧缩。这个版本的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm specification</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">不要求</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在位置，对编译过的代码管理也没有限制。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以是固定的大小，也可以根据估算扩展或紧缩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的内存可以是不连续的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A Java virtual machine implementation may provide the programmer or the user control over the initial size of the method area, as well as, in the case of a varying-size method area, control over the maximum and minimum method area size</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的实现可能支持开发人员或者用户控制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的初始大小，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可变的情况下，可以控制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的最大最小值。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">也产生一种异常：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">若</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中的内存不能满足分配请求的要求，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">抛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OutOfMemoryError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">5. Runtime Constant Pool</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; A runtime constant pool is a per-class or per-interface runtime representation of the Constant_pool table in a class file. It contains several kinds of constants, ranging from numeric literals known at compile time to method and field references that must be resolved at run time. The runtime constant pool serves a function similar to that of a symbol table for a conventional programming language, although it contains a wider range of data than a typical symbol table.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Runtime Constant Pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">是代表运行时每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">文件中的常量表。它包括几种常量：编译期的数字常量、方法或者域的引用（在运行时解析）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">runtime constant pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的功能类似于传统编程语言的符号表，尽管它包含的数据比典型的符号表要丰富的多。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; Each runtime constant pool is allocated from the Java virtual machine\'s method area. The runtime constant pool for a class or interface is constructed when the class or interface is created by the Java virtual machine.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Runtime Constant pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">都是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中分配的，每个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">或者</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">interface</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">constant pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">都是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">或接口的时候创建的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在构建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">interface</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">constant pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的时候，会产生以下异常：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在创建</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">class</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">或</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">interface</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的时候，若</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">method area</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可用内存空间满足不了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">constant pool</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">构建所需要的内存空间，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">则会抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OutOfMemoryError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">6. Native Method Stacks</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; An implementation of the Java virtual machine may use conventional stacks, colloquially called &quot;C stacks,&quot; to support Native methods, methods written in a language other than the Java programming language. Native method stacks may also be used by the implementation of an interpreter for the Java virtual machine\'s instruction set in a language such as C. Java virtual machine implementations that cannot load Native methods and that do not themselves rely on conventional stacks need not supply native method stacks. If supplied, native method stacks are typically allocated per thread when each thread is created.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">若</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">提供</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Native method Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">native method stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在每个线程创建的时候进行分配</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; The Java virtual machine specification permits native method stacks either to be of a fixed size or to dynamically expand and contract as required by the computation. If the native method stacks are of a fixed size, the size of each native method stack may be chosen independently when that stack is created. In any case, a Java virtual machine implementation may provide the programmer or the user control over the initial size of the native method stacks. In the case of varying-size native method stacks, it may also make available control over the maximum and minimum method stack sizes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Native Method Stacks</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会产生以下两种异常：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">若一个线程估算需要较大的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">native method stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，超出了允许范围，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">则会抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">StackOverflowError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">如果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">native method stacks</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">可以动态扩展，当线程企图扩展但是没有足够的内存实现这种扩展，或者没有足够的内存为新的线程分配初始的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Native Method Stack</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">空间时，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">jvm</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">会抛出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">OutOfMemoryError.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;堆内存分配</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; JVM初始分配的内存由-Xms指定，默认是物理内存的1/64;JVM最大分配的内存由-Xmx指 定，默认是物理内存的1/4.默认空余堆内存小于40%时，JVM就会增大堆直到-Xmx的最大限制；空余堆内存大于70%时，JVM会减少堆直到 -Xms的最小限制。因此</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://server.chinaitlab.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 22px;\">服务器</a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">一般设置-Xms、-Xmx相等以避免在每次GC 后调整堆的大小。对象的堆内存由称为垃圾回收器的自动内存管理系统回收。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922123868.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922123868.png\" width=\"567\" height=\"214\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922123868.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;</a></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922131434.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922131434.png\" width=\"633\" height=\"253\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922131434.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;</a><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 非堆内存分配</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; JVM使用-XX:PermSize设置非堆内存初始值，默认是物理内存的1/64;由XX:MaxPermSize设置最大非堆内存的大小，默认是物理内存的1/4.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922134598.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922134598.png\" width=\"649\" height=\"284\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><a href=\"http://java.chinaitlab.com/UploadFiles_8734/201205/2012050922134598.png\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;</a><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; JVM内存限制（最大值）</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; JVM内存的最大值跟操作系统有很大的关系。简单的说就32位处理器虽然 可控内存空间有4GB,但是具体的操作系统会给一个限制，这个限制一般是2GB-3GB（一般来说</span><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://windows.chinaitlab.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 255); line-height: 22px;\">Windows</a><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">系统下为1.5G-2G,Linux系统 下为2G-3G），而64bit以上的处理器就不会有限制了。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">关于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">虚拟机的更详细的规范请看</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br />\r\nsun</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">网站对虚拟机规范的介绍</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The java Virtual Machine Specification&nbsp;<br />\r\nhttp://java.sun.com/docs/books/jvms/second_edition/html/VMSpecTOC.doc.html</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-21 17:30:08'),(54,48,'Java中为什么String是不可变的','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;\r\ncolor:#222222;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">This is an old yet still popular question. There are multiple reasons that String is designed to be immutable in Java. A good answer depends on good understanding of memory, synchronization, data structures, etc. In the following, I will summarize some answers.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial;\">1. Requirement of String Pool</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">String pool (String intern pool) is a special storage area in Java heap. When a string is created and if the string already exists in the pool, the reference of the existing string will be returned, instead of creating a new object and returning its reference.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">The following code will create only one string object in the heap.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">String string1 = &quot;abcd&quot;;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">String string2 = &quot;abcd&quot;;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Here is how it looks:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><a href=\"http://www.programcreek.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/java-string-pool.jpeg\"><span style=\"color:#03398F;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\r\nid=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\r\npath=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n<v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\" />\r\n<v:formulas>\r\n<v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\" />\r\n<v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\" />\r\n</v:formulas>\r\n<v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\" />\r\n<o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\" />\r\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1025\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"java-string-pool\"\r\nhref=\"http://www.programcreek.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/java-string-pool.jpeg\"\r\nstyle=\'width:300pt;height:195pt\' o:button=\"t\">\r\n<v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\lenovo\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\msohtml1\\01\\clip_image001.jpg\"\r\no:href=\"http://www.programcreek.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/java-string-pool.jpeg\" />\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img border=\"0\" width=\"400\" height=\"260\" src=\"http://www.programcreek.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/java-string-pool.jpeg\" alt=\"java-string-pool\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-8731\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_i1025\" /><!--[endif]--></span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">If string is not immutable, changing the string with one reference will lead to the wrong value for the other references.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial;\">2. Allow String to Cache its Hashcode<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">The hashcode of string is frequently used in Java. For example, in a HashMap. Being immutable guarantees that hashcode will always the same, so that it can be cashed without worrying the changes.That means, there is no need to calculate hashcode every time it is used. This is more efficient.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">In String class, it has the following code:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"641\" style=\"width:480.9pt;\r\n    mso-cellspacing:1.5pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"background:#FF9933;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">private</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> <b>int</b> hash</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#339933;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">;</span><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">//this   is used to cache hash code.</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial;\">3. Security<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">String is widely used as parameter for many java classes, e.g. network connection, opening files, etc. Were String not immutable, a connection or file would be changed and lead to serious security threat. The method thought it was connecting to one machine, but was not. Mutable strings could cause security problem in Reflection too, as the parameters are strings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">Here is a code example:I<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"641\" style=\"width:480.9pt;\r\n    mso-cellspacing:1.5pt\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"background:#FF9933;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">boolean</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> connect</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">string s</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">){</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">if</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#339933;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">!</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">isSecure</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">s</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">))</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">{</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">throw</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\">new</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#003399;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">SecurityException</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">()</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#339933;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"> <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">}</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   </span><i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\n            mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#666666;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">//here will cause   problem, if s is changed before this by using other references.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   causeProblem</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">(</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">s</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#009900;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\">)</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\n            font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#339933;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#000066;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\n            color:#009900;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">}</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:#000066;\r\n            mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">n summary, the reasons include design, efficiency, and security. Actually, this is also true for many other &ldquo;why&rdquo; questions in a Java interview.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">from:<a href=\"http://www.programcreek.com/2013/04/why-string-is-immutable-in-java/\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Arial\">http://www.programcreek.com/2013/04/why-string-is-immutable-in-java/</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">附：</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体; line-height: 22px;\">String是所有语言中最常用的一个类。我们知道在Java中，String是不可变的、final的。Java在运行时也保存了一个字符串池(String pool)，这使得String成为了一个特别的类。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 11px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体; line-height: 14px; color: rgb(25, 25, 25);\"><a name=\"string%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%84\" href=\"https://github.com/stephanietang/ImportNew/blob/master/Java/Why%20String%20is%20immutable.md#string%E7%B1%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E5%A4%84\" class=\"external\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; border-color: rgb(8, 155, 195); color: rgb(8, 155, 195);\"></a>String类不可变性的好处</h3>\r\n<ol style=\"margin: 10px 0px 10px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251); list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体; line-height: 22px;\">\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">只有当字符串是不可变的，字符串池才有可能实现。字符串池的实现可以在运行时节约很多heap空间，因为不同的字符串变量都指向池中的同一个字符串。但如果字符串是可变的，那么String interning将不能实现(译者注：<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/String_interning\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; outline: none; text-decoration: none; border-color: rgb(8, 155, 195); color: rgb(8, 155, 195);\">String interning</a>是指对不同的字符串仅仅只保存一个，即不会保存多个相同的字符串。)，因为这样的话，如果变量改变了它的值，那么其它指向这个值的变量的值也会一起改变。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">如果字符串是可变的，那么会引起很严重的安全问题。譬如，数据库的用户名、密码都是以字符串的形式传入来获得数据库的连接，或者在socket编程中，主机名和端口都是以字符串的形式传入。因为字符串是不可变的，所以它的值是不可改变的，否则黑客们可以钻到空子，改变字符串指向的对象的值，造成安全漏洞。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">因为字符串是不可变的，所以是多线程安全的，同一个字符串实例可以被多个线程共享。这样便不用因为线程安全问题而使用同步。字符串自己便是线程安全的。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">类加载器要用到字符串，不可变性提供了安全性，以便正确的类被加载。譬如你想加载java.sql.Connection类，而这个值被改成了myhacked.Connection，那么会对你的数据库造成不可知的破坏。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;\">因为字符串是不可变的，所以在它创建的时候hashcode就被缓存了，不需要重新计算。这就使得字符串很适合作为Map中的键，字符串的处理速度要快过其它的键对象。这就是HashMap中的键往往都使用字符串。</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15pt; line-height: 16.3pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:Helvetica;color:#222222;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-21 17:35:51'),(55,38,'雷军和周鴻祎：青春不会被浪費','<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Verdana, \'BitStream vera Sans\', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">汽车之家创始人李想很早就出名了。触控科技创始人陈昊芝近两年因為《捕魚达人》才成了明星。陈昊芝說：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>我跟李想十几年前就认识，做个人网站而言，他是我小弟。他是把一件事干了十几年，我是十几年干了很多事。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">不過陈昊芝只說了前半句，后半句沒好意思說出來：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>但，我最近的這一件事，一下子就赶上李想了。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">从<span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span>开始，陈昊芝参与、创办、或投资的公司有：卓越网，一家电商网站，联众，游戏点卡销售公司，爱卡汽车网，一家<span lang=\"EN-US\">SNS</span>社区网站，译言，盛世收藏网<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>盡皆失敗或中途放弃。直到<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>《捕鱼达人》上线，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>收入估计近<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>亿。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">李想的简历则简单。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1999</span>高中辞职做<span lang=\"EN-US\">IT</span>资讯网站，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span>做汽车资讯网站，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span>汽车之家收入据说过近<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>亿。如今李想和陈昊芝，说都在准备上市。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">问题：若陈昊芝之前沒那么些折騰，而直接瞄准移动游戏创业，会不会比現在更強大？答案很可能是否定。峰哥以為：之前所有折騰和失敗，为最后一次成功奠定基礎。換句話說，李想在产品资讯这个領域的长期耕耘，和陈昊芝在不同領域里的长期抓瞎，本质上都相同，都在积累和試錯。只是方式不同而已。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">青春是不会被浪費掉的。只要你在诚恳的前行。十多岁的年轻人，无论是在學校里上课，还是在大街上打群架，在少管所里被牢头欺負，都是宝贵经历，都埋藏下日后开花結果的養料。甚至，在大街和少管所里学到的，可能比學校里更多元和扎实。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">雷军和周鴻祎又何尝不如是。碰巧周鴻祎前两天说，失败了<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>次，然后成功<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>次，能不要那<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>次失败而直接成功吗？除非是马后炮。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">小米和<span lang=\"EN-US\">360</span>，不久前先后突破一百亿美金市值。成为仅次于<span lang=\"EN-US\">BAT</span>三大家的互联网勢力。不過其实倒過去几年，在小米还剛成立，就在还沒上市的<span lang=\"EN-US\">360</span>跟腾讯大打出手時，雷军和周鴻祎兩人的江湖地位和实际影響力，都明显高于大多數的互联网上市公司的创始人和<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>，只次于李彥宏、马云、马化腾三个被數百亿美金的公司市值支撐起來的大佬。只是這雷、周二人的地位和勢力並沒一個大公司和大市值作支撐。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">做<span lang=\"EN-US\">3721</span>再卖給雅虎，被周鴻祎自己称为<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>百亿美金的教訓<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。然后从雅虎负气出走，做<span lang=\"EN-US\">VC</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">360</span>最开始的階段做搜索、做社區等等，都失敗。这个階段，跟陈昊芝的折騰一回事。表面是挫折，实际是蓄勢。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>的<span lang=\"EN-US\">3Q</span>大戰，互联网上还有第二个敢跟腾讯打割喉战的人吗？这已是江湖勢力的标志。有人說，在那之前，周鴻祎曾跟一群行业朋友聚会后对着车頂发呆了很久，然后說：这个天花板，一定要捅破。在那之后，周鴻祎可能心里清楚，这个江湖沒人敢挡路了。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">雷军的故事絕对称得上励志。一个老公司做了<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>年，半死不活，然后心身俱疲而出走，做投资，到最后，<span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span>岁的人再创业，做一个全新模式，<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>年半搞到百亿美金市值，跻身巨头。江湖上人一直在传，雷军早先有心結、<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>不服氣<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>，这么老資格，这么聰明，还这么勤奮，但做不出如马化腾、丁磊這些后辈年輕人能做出的那样規模的事业。其實回過頭來看，沒必要不服气，只是折騰和试錯的時間要相對長。大器晚成的类型。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">年前听一個<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>說，他跟<span lang=\"EN-US\">BAT</span>三巨头的某个<span lang=\"EN-US\">co-founder</span>聊天，這位大佬表現出瞧不起雷军和周鴻祎这些人，說虽然他們有见识、有地位，但終究沒做出過大公司，<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>他們不知道一个真正的大事业是怎么做出來的<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">从现实角度。这两个人让行业看到一點：<span lang=\"EN-US\">BAT</span>的格局并非铁桶一般不可改变。一個是直接冲击，一個是另起路徑。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">从哲學角度。一個聰明而勤奋的青春，是不会被浪費的。价值終究会被呈現。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">最后說一下王兴，這也是典型。校內、海內、飯否，一路失敗。直到美团。之前王兴这个人在江湖里就受好評。眼光好，人品正，懂产品，不懈怠。但却为什么一直挫折。直到<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>，王兴把之前所有教訓和经验都用來打造一个沒短板的美团。比如，要現金流，不要只依靠<span lang=\"EN-US\">VC</span>；打平很重要，利润很重要；无论多少融資和多少次融資，创始团队都要控股；引入巨头投資但不被控股。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">青春不會被浪費掉。這是一個哲學命題。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体\">再回到陈昊芝那句話，该这样說：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">有的人，是把一件事儿干了十几年，就像李想和马化腾、李彥宏、马云。一門深入，需要机缘配合。有的人，是十几年干了很多事儿，受挫不断，但不必急，最后碰上一件事，就能把之前的教訓都用上，后來居上，大器晚成。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-11-22 16:05:27'),(56,47,'Linux中软连接和硬连接','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">链接有两种方式，软链接和硬链接。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">软链接文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">软链接又叫符号链接，这个文件包含了另一个文件的路径名。可以是任意文件或目录，可以链接不同文件系统的文件。链接文件甚至可以链接不存在的文件，这就产生一般称之为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">断链</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的问题</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">或曰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">现象</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&quot;)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，链接文件甚至可以循环链接自己。类似于编程语言中的递归。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">ln -s </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">命令可以生成一个软连接，如下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">[root@linux236 test]# ln -s source_file softlink_file<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在对符号文件进行读或写操作的时候，系统会自动把该操作转换为对源文件的操作，但删除链接文件时，系统仅仅删除链接文件，而不删除源文件本身。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">硬链接文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">info ln </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">命令告诉您，硬链接是已存在文件的另一个名字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">(A &quot;hard link&quot; is another name for an existing file)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">，这多少有些令人困惑。硬连接的命令是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">ln -d existfile newfile<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">硬链接文件有两个限制</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">1)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、不允许给目录创建硬链接；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">2)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">、只有在同一文件系统中的文件之间才能创建硬链接</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">对硬链接文件进行读写和删除操作时候，结果和软链接相同。但如果我们删除硬链接文件的源文件，硬链接文件仍然存在，而且保留了愿有的内容。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">这时，系统就</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">忘记</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">了它曾经是硬链接文件。而把他当成一个普通文件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:45.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 45.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">两者之间的区别</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">硬连接指通过索引节点来进行的连接。在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的文件系统中，保存在磁盘分区中的文件不管是什么类型都给它分配一个编号，称为索引节点号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">(Inode Number)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中，多个文件名指向同一索引节点是存在的。一般这种连接就是硬连接。硬连接的作用是允许一个文件拥有多个有效路径名，这样用户就可以建立硬连接到重要文件</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">以防止</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">误删</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的功能。其原因如上所述，因为对应该目录的索引节点有一个以上的连接。只删除一个连接并不影响索引节点本身和其它的连接，只有当最后一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">连接被删除后，文件的数据块及目录的连接才会被释放。也就是说，文件才会被真正删除。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">软链接文件有点类似于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Windows</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">的快捷方式。它实际上是特殊文件的一种。在符号连接中，文件实际上是一个文本文件，其中包含的有另一文件的位置信息</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">首先要弄清楚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">系统中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">,</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">内核为每一个新创建的文件分配一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Inode(</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">索引结点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">),</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">每个文件都有一个惟一的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">inode</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">号。文件属性保存在索引结点里，在访问文件时，索引结点被复制到内存，从而实现文件的快速访问。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">链接是一种在共享文件和访问它的用户的若干目录项之间建立联系的一种方法。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Linux</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">中包括两种链接：硬链接</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">(Hard Link)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">和软链接</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">(Soft Link),</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">软链接又称为符号链接（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">Symbolic link</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2013-12-03 15:35:35'),(57,45,'Mysql自查大全','<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 21pt;\">建库</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;create database xx charset=utf8 collate utf8_general_ci;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;